%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%E2%80%99s%20WTO%20Stance%20on%20Farmers%20Will%20Be%20a%20Test%20of%20Its%20Rhetoric%20of%20Championing%20the%20Global%20South%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F01132506%2FAgriculture_main.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lofty%20rhetoric%20of%20championing%20the%20Global%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F09%2F12%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Findia-china-global-south.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESouth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20realm%20of%20trade%20issues%20faces%20an%20ugly%20test%2C%20both%20domestically%20and%20at%20an%20upcoming%20trade%20summit.%20The%20government%20is%20now%20embroiled%20in%20a%20fierce%20negotiating%20battle%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D14zW4nl6bMs%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efarmers%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20have%20presented%20a%20dozen%20demands%2C%20particularly%20focusing%20on%20guaranteeing%20minimum%20support%20prices%20(MSP)%20and%20halting%20agri-corporatisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIronically%2C%20on%20a%20day%20when%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fformer-pm-pv-narasimha-rao-chaudhary-charan-singh-and-dr-ms-swaminathan-to-get-bharat-ratna-pm-modi%2Farticleshow%2F107549332.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ebestowed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20highest%20award%20of%20the%20land%2C%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%2C%20upon%20the%20late%20M.S.%20Swaminathan%2C%20farmers%20demanded%20the%20implementation%20of%20reforms%20he%20had%20advocated%20to%20uplift%20millions%20of%20struggling%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Fpolicy%2Freport-summaries%2Fswaminathan-report-national-commission-farmers%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSwaminathan%252C%2520submitted%2520five%2520reports%2520through%2Cholistic%2520national%2520policy%2520for%2520farmers.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efarmers%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20farmers%E2%80%99%20demands%2C%20both%20symbolically%20and%20practically%2C%20mirror%20the%20concerns%20of%20developing%20countries%20in%20the%20global%20farm%20trade.%20If%20the%20long-standing%20demands%20of%20the%20Indian%20farmers%20are%20seemingly%20buried%20under%20one%20pretext%20or%20the%20other%2C%20then%2C%20how%20can%20the%20Modi%20government%20effectively%20press%20its%20much-delayed%20demand%20for%20a%20permanent%20solution%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fbusiness%2Fpermanent-solution-for-public-stockholding-top-priority-for-india-9116333%2F%5C%22%3Epublic%20stockholding%3C%2Fa%3E%20(PSH)%20programmes%20for%20food%20security%2C%20in%20which%20the%20MSP%20is%20a%20critical%20component.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECome%20February%2026%2C%20more%20than%201%2C000%20delegations%20will%20gather%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%20for%20the%20World%20Trade%20Organisation%E2%80%99s%20biennial%20trade%20ministerial%20conference.%20The%2013th%20ministerial%20conference%20(MC%2013)%20of%20the%20trade%20body%20will%20decide%20whether%20there%20is%20any%20future%20for%20the%20much-fragmented%20multilateral%20trading%20system.%20It%20will%20also%20indicate%20whether%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20developing%20countries%20in%20agriculture%20will%20ever%20be%20met.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20letter%20sent%20to%20trade%20ministers%20on%20January%2031%2C%20the%20WTO%E2%80%99s%20Director-General%2C%20Ngozi%20Okonjo-Iweala%2C%20who%20carries%20a%20dual-passport%20of%20Nigeria%20and%20the%20United%20States%2C%20writes%3A%20%E2%80%9COver%2050%20countries%20will%20be%20undergoing%20elections%2C%20including%20in%20very%20large%20democracies.%20People%20around%20the%20world%20are%20feeling%20anxious%20about%20their%20cost%20of%20living%2C%20and%20about%20the%20future.%20The%20WTO%20must%20be%20cognizant%20of%20the%20challenges%2C%20and%20we%20must%20do%20our%20part%20to%20contribute%20to%20reinvigorating%20growth%20and%20opportunities%20for%20people%20everywhere.%20MC13%20presents%20an%20immediate%20opportunity%20for%20ministers%20to%20show%20the%20world%20that%20it%20can%20get%20results%20on%20issues%20that%20matter%20for%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20behind%20closed%20doors%2C%20there%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20sustained%20push%20on%20plurilateral%20issues%20that%20are%20being%20pushed%20by%20the%20US%2C%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20and%20China%2C%20without%20any%20prior%20multilateral%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwn.my%2Ftitle2%2Fwto.info%2F2024%2Fti240108.htm%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Econsensus%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20issues%20that%20concerns%20a%20large%20majority%20of%20people%20in%20the%20world%20is%20food%20security%20and%20the%20governments%E2%80%99%20ability%20to%20guarantee%20the%20provision%20of%20food.%20And%20there%20is%20certainly%20no%20bigger%20issue%20than%20providing%20bread%20on%20the%20table%20for%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20starving%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20can%20only%20be%20done%20by%20changing%20existing%20global%20trade%20rules%20that%20were%20negotiated%20at%20the%20height%20of%20the%20globalisation%20in%20the%20mid-80s%20through%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wto.org%2Fenglish%2Fthewto_e%2Fwhatis_e%2Ftif_e%2Ffact5_e.htm%5C%22%3EUruguay%20Round%20commitments%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20rules%20are%20proven%20to%20be%20asymmetrical%20and%20unfair%20to%20developing%20countries%20through%20numerous%20studies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20the%20urgency%20of%20the%20matter%2C%20the%20US%2C%20which%20continues%20to%20be%20the%20biggest%20beneficiary%20of%20the%20Uruguay%20Round%20commitments%2C%20along%20with%20the%20EU%2C%20Japan%2C%20Switzerland%2C%20Norway%2C%20and%20Canada%20among%20others%20are%20prepared%20to%20go%20to%20any%20extent%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwn.my%2Ftitle2%2Fwto.info%2F2024%2Fti240207.htm%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eblock%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20attempts%20to%20rewrite%20those%20rules.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20permanent%20solution%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgainst%20this%20backdrop%2C%20the%20constant%20claim%20of%20leading%20the%20Global%20South%20faces%20a%20test%20not%20just%20at%20home%20but%20abroad%20as%20well.%20It%20will%20become%20clear%20whether%20India%20fights%20for%20its%20farmers%20or%20yields%20ground%20to%20Uncle%20Sam%20on%20one%20of%20the%20most%20crucial%20issues%20for%20poor%20farmers%20in%20developing%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20issue%20lies%20the%20pursuit%20of%20a%20permanent%20solution%20for%20public%20stockholding%20programmes%20for%20food%20security%20purposes%20in%20developing%20countries.%20Washington%20remains%20violently%20opposed%20to%20the%20permanent%20solution%20as%20its%20powerful%20farm%20lobbies%20are%20unhappy%20with%20the%20existing%20peace%20clause%20or%20interim%20solution%20that%20was%20decided%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.wto.org%2Fdol2fe%2FPages%2FSS%2Fdirectdoc.aspx%3Ffilename%3Dq%3A%2FWT%2FMIN13%2F38.pdf%26Open%3DTrue%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E2013%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20was%20later%20reinforced%20in%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wto.org%2Fenglish%2Fthewto_e%2Fminist_e%2Fmc9_e%2Fnov14stockholding_e.htm%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E2014%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20decided%20that%20the%20peace%20clause%20for%20exempting%20public%20stockholding%20programmes%20from%20legal%20scrutiny%20will%20continue%20as%20long%20as%20countries%20agreed%20to%20a%20permanent%20solution%20which%20ought%20to%20have%20been%20concluded%20in%202015%20and%20then%20deferred%20to%202017.%20The%20US%2C%20however%2C%20chose%20to%20block%20any%20decision%20for%20the%20past%20eight%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20discussions%20on%20a%20draft%20text%20issued%20by%20the%20chair%20from%20Turkey%20on%20January%2029%2C%20the%20US%2C%20along%20with%20supporters%20like%20Paraguay%2C%20proposed%20deleting%20the%20option%20to%20conclude%20an%20outcome%20on%20the%20permanent%20solution%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwn.my%2Ftitle2%2Fwto.info%2F2024%2Fti240205.htm%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAbu%20Dhabi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Instead%2C%20it%20suggested%20continuing%20discussions%20on%20several%20issues%20in%20the%20agriculture%20dossier%20until%20the%20WTO%E2%80%99s%2014th%20ministerial%20conference%20in%20Cameroon%20in%202026%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20US%20reckons%20that%20the%20peace%20clause%20has%20enabled%20India%20to%20become%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20exporters%20of%20rice%2C%20an%20item%20on%20which%20India%20has%20also%20exceeded%20its%20de%20minimis%20limit%20of%2010%25%20during%202021%20and%202022.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%5BUnder%20WTO%20rules%2C%20member%20countries%20are%20required%20to%20limit%20the%20amount%20of%20domestic%20support%20they%20provide%20to%20their%20agricultural%20producers%2C%20as%20excessive%20subsidies%20can%20distort%20international%20trade.%20The%20de%20minimis%20level%20represents%20a%20threshold%20below%20which%20subsidies%20are%20considered%20insignificant%20and%20do%20not%20count%20toward%20the%20total%20allowable%20support.%5D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20PSH%20has%20helped%20India%20in%20addressing%20the%20provision%20of%20cereals%20like%20rice%20and%20wheat%2C%20which%20are%20procured%20through%20MSP%20and%20sold%20below%20MSP%20at%20lower%20prices.%20Without%20such%20a%20scheme%2C%20the%20poverty%20levels%20in%20India%2C%20which%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbesindia.com%2Farticle%2Fexplainers%2Fpoverty-rate-in-india%2F90117%2F1%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%25202023%2520Multidimensional%2520Poverty%2520Index%2Cthe%2520increase%2520in%2520extreme%2520poverty.%5C%22%3Eamong%20the%20highest%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20would%20have%20shot%20through%20the%20roof.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20US%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20Brazil%20among%20others%20liken%20the%20PSH%20programme%20to%20a%20market%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bing.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3DUS%2Balleges%2BIndia%2Bprovides%2Bmarket%2Bprice%2Bsupport%2Bfor%2Brice%26qs%3Dn%26form%3DQBRE%26sp%3D-1%26ghc%3D1%26lq%3D0%26pq%3Dus%2Balleges%2Bindia%2Bprovides%2Bmarket%2Bprice%2Bsupport%2Bfor%2Brice%26sc%3D11-55%26sk%3D%26cvid%3DADBDC5E79C7A4F17915B62822B15DEF4%26ghsh%3D0%26ghacc%3D0%26ghpl%3D%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eprice%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20support%20scheme%20and%20insist%20that%20it%20is%20a%20breach%20of%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20commitments.%20However%2C%20the%20calculation%20of%20the%20market%20price%20support%20programmes%20in%20the%20case%20of%20India%20is%20flawed%20as%20they%20are%20based%20on%20static%20assumptions%20like%20external%20reference%20price%20(ERP)%20based%20on%201986-88%20prices.%20Umpteen%20attempts%20to%20change%20the%20ERP%2C%20a%20demand%20developing%20countries%20have%20raised%20time%20and%20time%20again%20since%202015%2C%20are%20blocked%20by%20the%20US.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20developing%20countries%2C%20particularly%20members%20of%20the%20G33%20countries%20led%20by%20Indonesia%20and%20the%20Africa%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twn.my%2Ftitle2%2Fwto.info%2F2023%2Fti231209.htm%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EGroup%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20have%20repeatedly%20demanded%20a%20permanent%20solution.%20However%2C%20they%20look%20up%20to%20India%20to%20do%20the%20heavy%20lifting%20because%20of%20the%20allegedly%20political%2Fdiplomatic%2Fnegotiating%20arm-twisting%20that%20goes%20behind%20the%20ministerial%20conferences.%20It%20has%20been%20seemingly%20established%20that%20the%20powerful%20members%20and%20the%20WTO%20Secretariat%20ensure%20that%20issues%20raised%20by%20the%20developing%20countries%20are%20often%20pushed%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eback%20burner%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20groundwork%20for%20a%20permanent%20solution%20for%20PSH%20programmes%20for%20food%20security%20purposes%20has%20been%20laid%20ably%20by%20the%20Indian%20negotiators%2C%20who%20finally%20succeeded%20in%20including%20the%20first%20option%20in%20the%20chair%E2%80%99s%20draft%20text%20for%20the%20permanent%20solution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%2C%20it%20now%20depends%20on%20the%20political%20masters.%20Piyush%20Goyal%2C%20the%20commerce%20minister%2C%20is%20currently%20negotiating%20with%20farmers%20back%20home%20to%20ensure%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20bloated%20rhetoric%20championing%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20but%20concrete%20outcomes%20echoed%20through%20such%20pronouncements.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20far%2C%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20track%20record%20for%20accomplishing%20its%20trade%20commitments%20appears%20somewhat%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epw.in%2Fjournal%2F2016%2F11%2Finsight%2Fwhat-happened-nairobi-and-why.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eappalling%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20current%20finance%20minister%2C%20who%20was%20the%20commerce%20minister%20in%202015%2C%20has%20surrendered%20the%20ground%20to%20the%20US%20without%20a%20fight.%20With%20elections%20to%20be%20held%20in%20the%20next%20two-and-half%20months%2C%20it%20would%20be%20interesting%20to%20see%20if%20the%20current%20regime%20stands%20for%20its%20farmers%20or%20leaves%20them%20high%20and%20dry%20both%20domestically%20and%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707659736000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findias-wto-stance-on-farmers-will-be-a-test-of-its-rhetoric-of-championing-the-global-south%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20the%20upcoming%20WTO's%20biennial%20trade%20ministerial%20conference%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%2C%20it%20will%20become%20clear%20whether%20India%20fights%20for%20its%20farmers%20or%20yields%20ground%20to%20Uncle%20Sam%20on%20one%20of%20the%20most%20crucial%20issues%20for%20poor%20farmers%20in%20developing%20countries.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gavaskar%20on%20how%20Starc%20can%20justify%20his%20hefty%20IPL%20price%20tag%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707659195000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107603978%2Cimgsize-61438.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fipl%2Ftop-stories%2Fif-starc-can-sunil-gavaskar-on-how-aussie-pacer-can-justify-his-hefty-ipl-price-tag%2Farticleshow%2F107603723.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders'%20whopping%20IPL%20bid%20of%20Rs%2024.75%20crore%20for%20Australian%20pacer%20Mitchell%20Starc%20surprised%20the%20cricketing%20community.%20Even%20the%20legendary%20Indian%20cricketer%20Sunil%20Gavaskar%20expressed%20his%20opinion%2C%20stating%20that%20no%20player%20is%20deserving%20of%20such%20a%20substantial%20amount.%20Gavaskar%20added%20that%20Starc%20will%20need%20to%20deliver%20an%20exceptional%20performance%20in%20the%20IPL%202024%20to%20justify%20the%20hefty%20paycheque.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fipl%2Ftop-stories%2Fif-starc-can-sunil-gavaskar-on-how-aussie-pacer-can-justify-his-hefty-ipl-price-tag%2Farticleshow%2F107603723.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20studied%20at%20Yale%20and%20Cambridge%20University.%20