cles%20in%20rates%2C%20inflation%2C%20economic%20growth%20trends%2C%26quot%3B%20Subramanian%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%26quot%3BTake%20the%20road%20less%20traveled.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20stock%20market%20is%20highly%20efficient%2C%20but%20less-so%20for%20companies%20that%20receive%20less%20research%20coverage%20from%20Wall%20Street.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20less%20efficient%20stocks%20have%20more%20outsize%20opportunities%20and%20risks%20compared%20to%20a%20company%20that%20is%20tracked%20and%20owned%20by%20nearly%20everyone%20on%20Wall%20Street.%20That%20suggests%20investors%20should%20focus%20their%20investments%20on%20less%20popular%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20limited%20our%20universe%20to%20stocks%20with%20lower%20sell-side%20analyst%20coverage%20%E2%80%93%20arguably%20a%20less%20efficient%20universe%20%E2%80%93%20fundamental%20factors'%20performance%20dramatically%20improved%2C%26quot%3B%20Subramanian%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%26quot%3BExtend%20your%20time%20horizons.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20rise%20of%20zero-day%20options%2C%20investors%20are%20getting%20more%20and%20more%20short-sighted%2C%20trying%20to%20make%20a%20quick%20buck.%20But%20that's%20not%20a%20sustainable%20practice%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20investing%2C%20especially%20if%20you're%20trying%20to%20outperform%20the%20broader%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20investors%20have%20collectively%20moved%20to%20the%20short-term%20%E2%80%93%20we%20remind%20ourselves%20that%20the%20likelihood%20of%20losing%20money%20in%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20drops%20from%20a%20coin%20flip%20to%20a%202-sigma%20event%20by%20extending%20one's%20holding%20period%20from%20a%20day%20to%20a%20decade%2C%26quot%3B%20Subramanian%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETime%20is%20on%20an%20investor's%20side%2C%20as%20long%20as%20they%20take%20advantage%20of%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22664%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22stock%20market%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22