as%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEntering%20the%20prison%20reminded%20me%20of%20going%20through%20airport%20security%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22sign%20posted%20to%20the%20side%20of%20a%20brick%20wall%20pointing%20toward%20the%20security%20check%20in%20area%20for%20the%20clink%20restaurant%20at%20brixton%20prison%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd2b2643bb77284ba31d74%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20had%20to%20go%20through%20security%20before%20entering%20the%20restaurant.%20%3Cp%3EEibhlis%20Gale-Coleman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20unique%20aspect%20of%20dining%20at%20The%20Clink%20is%20entering%20the%20prison%20itself.%20I've%20never%20seen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fday-in-the-life-trans-woman-georgia-prison-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einside%20a%20working%20prison%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20experience%20began%20when%20I%20arrived%20outside%20the%20Brixton%20doors.%20I%20stopped%20at%20the%20portacabin%20on%20the%20opposite%20side%20of%20the%20road%20so%20the%20staff%20could%20store%20my%20bag%20and%20give%20me%20a%20lanyard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20staff%20may%20also%20offer%20replacement%20clothing%20if%20your%20outfit%20is%20deemed%20unsuitable.%20Most%20hats%2C%20scarves%2C%20gloves%2C%20miniskirts%2C%20ripped%20jeans%2C%20open-toe%20footwear%2C%20and%20clothing%20with%20sports%20logos%20%E2%80%94%20among%20other%20restrictions%20%E2%80%94%20are%20not%20permitted%2C%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheclinkcharity.org%2Ftheclinkcharity%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2FDress-Code-The-Clink-at-HMP-Brixton-FINAL-VERSION.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erestaurant's%20dress%20code%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20you%20and%20your%20bank%20card%20are%20permitted%20into%20the%20restaurant%2C%20meaning%20even%20