%20answer%20is%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20my%20family%2C%20we're%20all%20Arkins.%26quot%3B%20Then%20I%20could%20see%20the%20disappointment%20in%20their%20faces%20when%20I%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BJust%20not%20those%20Arkins.%26quot%3B%20As%20if%20that%20wasn't%20bad%20enough%2C%20even%20when%20properly%20introduced%2C%20people%20would%20inevitably%20call%20me%20Alan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20Christmas%20Eve%2C%20I%20was%20rushing%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdanielle-fishel-gift-wrapper-bloomingdales-after-boy-meets-world-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomingdales%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20buying%20a%20present%20for%20my%20father.%20When%20I%20handed%20my%20credit%20card%20to%20the%20saleswoman%2C%20she%20looked%20at%20the%20name%20and%20asked%20the%20usual%20question.%20Tired%20and%20cranky%2C%20I%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYes.%26quot%3B%20Then%20I%20leaned%20in%20and%20whispered%2C%20%26quot%3BThat%20gift%20you're%20wrapping%3F%20That's%20for%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20eyes%20widened%2C%20and%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe's%20one%20of%20my%20favorites.%26quot%3B%20Inspired%20by%20the%20near%20brush%20with%20celebrity%2C%20the%20tip%20of%20her%20tongue%20protruded%20between%20her%20lips%20as%20she%20meticulously%20concentrated%20on%20adorning%20the%20box%20with%20such%20elaborate%20decoration%20that%20it%20should%20have%20been%20placed%20in%20the%20store's%20window%20instead%20of%20my%20shopping%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EArkin%20himself%20once%20asked%20me%20if%20we%20could%20be%20related%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Alan's%20son%2C%20Adam%2C%20gained%20popularity%20starring%20in%20the%201990s%20TV%20series%C2%A0%26quot%3BChicago%20Hope%26quot%3B%20questions%20about%20my%20identity%20became%20even%20more%20frequent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20that%20time%2C%20I%20went%20to%20work%20as%20an%20executive%20at%20Paramount%20Pictures%2C%20and%20some%20people%20assumed%20that%20nepotism%20may%20have%20played%20a%20part%20in%20my%20obta