genous%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpoche.centre.uq.edu.au%2Fteam%2Flets-yarn-about-sleep%5C%22%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20Yarn%20About%20Sleep%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20Australia%E2%80%99s%20first%20sleep%20programme%20that%20addresses%20the%20current%20challenges%20in%20sleep%20health%20promotion%20and%20service%20delivery%20in%20Australian%20Indigenous%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20programme%20was%20designed%20in%20consultation%20with%20community%20members%2C%20service%20providers%20and%20health%20professionals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20consultations%20highlighted%20that%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20physical%20and%20mental%20health%20impact%2C%20for%20Indigenous%20peoples%2C%20sleep%20also%20impacts%20their%20spiritual%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuided%20by%20these%20rich%20conversations%2C%20the%20programme%20integrated%20scientific%20evidence%20on%20sleep%20health%20with%20Indigenous%20cultural%20and%20traditional%20knowledge%20to%20address%20behavioural%20sleep%20issues%20in%20teenagers%2C%20including%20delayed%20bedtime%2C%20excessive%20use%20of%20devices%20and%20inconsistent%20sleep%20and%20wake%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20programme%20offers%20visual%20tools%2C%20such%20as%20totem%20animal%20artworks%20to%20explain%20the%20impact%20of%20sleep%20loss%20on%20different%20body%20parts%20and%20functions%2C%20a%20walk%20on%20Country%20to%20learn%20about%20bush%20food%20and%20bush%20medicine%20to%20improve%20sleep%2C%20Indigenous%20relaxation%20training%20and%20Dreamtime%20stories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20priority%20of%20the%20programme%20is%20to%20strengthen%20local%20capacity%20for%20sleep%20health%20service%20delivery.%20The%20programme%20has%20trained%20Indigenous%20sleep%20coaches%20to%20help%20community%20members%20get%20a%20good%20night%E2%80%99s%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sleep%20coaches%20work%20with%20participants%20to%20understand%20contextual%2C%20behavioural%20and%20health-related%20factors%20affecting%20their%20ability%20to%20get%20a%20good%20night%E2%80%99s%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20this%20information%2C%20the%20sleep%20coach%20helps%20the%20participant%20identify%20sleep%20health%20goals%20they%E2%80%99d%20like%20to%20achieve%20from%20the%20programme%20and%20supports%20the%20participant%20in%20achieving%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20programme%20primarily%20focuses%20on%20introducing%20sleep%20health%2C%20a%20key%20component%20of%20the%20programme%20is%20strengthening%20cultural%20connections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20programme%20sessions%20includes%20a%20walk%20on%20Country%20helps%20participants%20get%20information%20on%20bush%20food%20and%20bush%20medicine%20to%20improve%20their%20sleep%20health.%20The%20last%20session%20covers%20an%20Indigenous%20relaxation%20training%2C%20Sleep%20for%20Strong%20Souls%2C%20that%20helps%20calm%20the%20mind%20and%20relax%20the%20body%20for%20good%20quality%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20programme%20has%20received%20unprecedented%20support%20from%20community%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20shown%20significant%20improvement%20in%20participants%E2%80%99%20knowledge%20and%20understanding%20of%20sleep%2C%20sleep%20hygiene%20and%20practices%20and%20a%20significant%20reduction%20in%20bedtime%20usage%20of%20electronic%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20schools%20have%20adopted%20the%20programme%20as%20a%20key%20extracurricular%20activity%20for%20improving%20students%E2%80%99%20sleep%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20now%20plans%20for%20other%20sleep-related%20projects%2C%20such%20as%20local%20diagnosis%20and%20management%20of%20obstructive%20sleep%20apnoea%2C%20which%20is%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelancet.com%2Fjournals%2Flanwpc%2Farticle%2FPIIS2666-6065(22)00005-0%2Ffulltext%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAcross%2520studies%2520compared%2520with%2520non%2Cpopulations%2520(39%252D46%2525)%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehighly%20prevalent%20yet%20significantly%20underdiagnosed%20condition%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20Indigenous%20Australians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAboriginal%20health%20workers%20are%20being%20trained%20to%20become%20sleep%20technologists%20to%20offer%20sleep%20apnoea%20care%20in%20Indigenous%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20also%20plans%20to%20provide%20a%20programme%20for%20young%20children%20and%20their%20families%20to%20establish%20healthy%20sleep%20habits%20from%20an%20early%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecognising%20the%20role%20of%20poor%20sleep%20in%20obesity%2C%20poor%20mental%20health%20and%20cardiovascular%20issues%2C%20sleep%20health%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20key%20priority%20for%20effective%20prevention%20and%20management%20of%20health%20issues%20in%20Indigenous%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProgrammes%20like%20this%20that%20privilege%20Indigenous%20voices%20and%20empower%20community%20members%20offer%20great%20potential%20for%20sustainable%20improvement%20in%20sleep%20and%20associated%20health%20outcomes%20for%20Indigenous%20peoples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EAssociate%20Professor%20Yaqoot%20Fatima%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20social%20epidemiologist%20and%20sleep%20scientist%20at%20the%20Poche%20Centre%20for%20Indigenous%20Health%2C%20University%20of%20Queensland.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3ERoslyn%20Von%20Senden%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20Kalkadoon%20woman%20from%20Mount%20Isa%2C%20Community%20Engagement%20Manager%20for%20the%20Let%E2%80%99s%20Yarn%20About%20Sleep%20programme%20and%20trainee%20sleep%20coach%20at%20the%20Poche%20Centre%20for%20Indigenous%20Health%2C%20University%20of%20Queensland.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EDr%20Daniel%20Sullivan%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20psychologist%20and%20sleep%20scientist%20at%20the%20Poche%20Centre%20for%20Indigenous%20Health%2C%20University%20of%20Queensland.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EThe%20research%20mentioned%20in%20this%20article%20has%20been%20supported%20by%20the%20Medical%20Research%20Future%