20to%20Italy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20shared%20three%20mistakes%20Americans%20make%20when%20moving%20to%20Italy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20Americans%20dream%20of%20moving%20to%20Italy%2C%20but%20it%20takes%20more%20than%20a%20plane%20ticket%20and%20spunk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20ask%20Patrizia%20Di%20Gregorio%2C%20an%20Italian-American%20who%20founded%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.expatslivinginrome.com%2Fabout-us%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20international%20social%20network%20Expats%20Living%20in%20Rome%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She's%20lived%20in%20Italy%20for%2023%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmericans%20want%20to%20come%20and%20don't%20understand%20that%20you%20can't%20just%20move%20to%20Italy%2C%26quot%3B%20Gregorio%2C%2052%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Patrizia%20Di%20Gregorio%20(Expats%20Living%20in%20Rome)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b976957a3d271488760434%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPatrizia%20Di%20Gregorio%20of%20Expats%20Living%20in%20Rome.%20%3Cp%3EPatrizia%20Di%20Gregorio%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.expatslivinginrome.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EExpats%20Living%20in%20Rome%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20become%20a%20lifeline%20for%20many%20potential%20and%20current%20expats%20navigating%20the%20sometimes%20confusing%20and%20arduous%20process%20of%20moving%20overseas.%20While%20the%20network%20provides%20resources%20for%20financial%20advice%20and%20immigration%20services%2C%20it%20also%20offers%20something%20crucial%20every%20expat%20needs%3A%20community.%20The%20Facebook%20group%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fexpatslivinginitaly%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EExpats%20Living%20in%20Italy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20connected%20to%20Expats%20Living%20in%20Rome%2C%20has%2092%2C800%20members%20and%20counting.%20Daily%2C%20people%20post%20questions%2C%20offer%20answers%2C%20and%20work%20through%20problems%20with%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGregorio%20told%20BI%20she%20noticed%20an%20uptick%20in%20expats%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Americans%20%E2%80%94%20interested%20in%20leaving%20the%20United%20States%20for%20Italy.%20American%20expats%20who%20spoke%20to%20BI%20pointed%20toward%20a%20number%20of%20factors%2C%20including%20political%20climate%20and%20the%20cost%20of%20retirement%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20a%20simple%20leap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGregorio%20shared%20three%20mistakes%20Americans%20make%20when%20moving%20to%20Italy.%20Take%20a%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20No.%201%20mistake%20Americans%20make%20when%20moving%20to%20Italy%20is%20having%20incomplete%20or%20incorrect%20paperwork%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221626%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Passport%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b979dd7a3d271488760570%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221060%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPassport.%3Cp%3ETetra%20Images%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGregorio%20explained%20that%20some%20American%20expats%20arrive%20in%20Italy%20without%20proper%20paperwork%2C%20including%20visas%20and%20other%20forms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20don't%20have%20all%20their%20paperwork%2C%20so%20they%20can't%20go%20right%20to%20city%20hall%20and%20apply%20for%20dual%20citizenship%2C%26quot%3B%20Gregorio%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fit.usembassy.gov%2Fu-s-citizen-services%2Flocal-resources-of-u-s-citizens%2Fvisiting-living%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20US%20Embassy%20%26amp%3B%20Consulates%20in%20Italy's%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%20notes%20that%20Americans%20staying%20in%20Italy%20for%20more%20than%20three%20months%20are%20considered%20residents%20and%20must%20obtain%20an%20entrance%20visa%20before%20arriving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20forms%20Americans%20may%20need%20to%20complete%20are%20the%20permesso%20di%20soggiorno%20(permit%20of%20stay)%20and%20accordo%20di%20integrazione%20(integration%20agreement).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGregorio%20said%20some%20Americans%20don't%20plan%20or%20budget%20their%20finances%20properly%2C%20leading%20to%20struggles%20in%20Italy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224288%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Euros.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b97a507a3d271488760590%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222848%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EProper%20budgeting%20is%20important%20before%20moving%20to%20Italy.%3Cp%3Eassalve%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Gregorio%2C%20splurging%20on%20big-ticket%20items%20in%20Italy%20without%20proper%20financial%20planning%20is%20a%20bad%20idea.%20It%20can%20feel%20magical%20to%20relocate%20to%20a%20new%20city%2C%20but%20it's%20important%20to%20be%20realistic%20about%20what%20you%20can%20afford%20and%20how%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Italy's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fconsnewyork.esteri.it%2Fen%2Fservizi-consolari-e-visti%2Fservizi-per-il-cittadino-straniero%2Fvisti%2Fvisas-to-enter-italy%2Felective-residency%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElective%20Residence%20visa%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20tailored%20for%20people%20with%20the%20financial%20means%20to%20support%20themselves%20autonomously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20rent%20luxury%20apartments%20and%20then%20find%20themselves%20broke%2C%26quot%3B%20Gregorio%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20it's%20like%2C%20'Why%20did%20you%20rent%20an%20apartment%20you%20can't%20afford%3F%20Didn't%20you%20think%20your%20savings%20were%20going%20to%20go%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESome%20Americans%20expect%20life%20in%20Italy%20to%20mimic%20their%20old%20one%20in%20the%20US%2C%20which%20creates%20unrealistic%20expectations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGregorio%20said%20some%20Americans%20move%20to%20Italy%20and%20don't%20take%20the%20proper%20steps%20to%20embrace%20the%20local%20culture.%20She%20said%20they%20expect%20%26quot%3Beverything%20to%20be%20just%20like%20home%20and%20then%20don't%20respond%20accordingly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20Italian%20guy%20said%20to%20me%2C%20'When%20Americans%20come%20to%20Italy%2C%20the%20American%20owns%20Italy.%20When%20an%20Italian%20goes%20to%20America%2C%20Americans%20still%20own%20America%2C'%26quot%3B%20Gregorio%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20it's%20helpful%20for%20American%20expats%20to%20be%20open-minded%20and%20learn%20to%20adapt%20to%20Italy's%20culture%20when%20they%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Patrizia%20Di%20Gregorio%20of%20Expats%20Living%20in%20Rome.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b978bf7a3d27148876052e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221470%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPatrizia%20Di%20Gregorio's%20Facebook%20pages%20are%20a%20popular%20hub%20for%20people%20moving%20to%20Italy.%3Cp%3EPatrizia%20Di%20Gregorio%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIntegrating%20into%20a%20new%20society%20can%20take%20some%20time%2C%20which%20is%20why%20it's%20so%20important%20to%20find%20a%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20need%20a%20network%20behind%20you%20that%20understands%20the%20intricacies%2C%26quot%3B%20Gregorio%20said.%20%26quot%3BJoining%20Facebook%20groups%20like%20Expats%20Living%20in%20Italy%20or%20others%20is%20a%20good%20source%20to%20learn%20from%20others%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20the%20mistakes%20they%20made.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-americans-make-when-moving-to-italy-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A17076