0buy%20discounted%20products%20within%20three%20months%20of%20expiration%20that%20other%20food%20sellers%20were%20put%20off%20by%2C%20Sherman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ET.J.%20Maxx%20doesn't%20sell%20fresh%20food%2C%20meaning%20the%20retailer%20doesn't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20getting%20frequent%20deliveries%20from%20suppliers%20and%20short%20expiry%20dates.%20Sherman%20said%20T.J.%20Maxx%20started%20out%20selling%20items%20like%20sauces%2C%20teas%2C%20and%20condiments%20but%20now%20focuses%20more%20on%20foreign%2C%20gourmet%2C%20and%20gifting%20foods%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20fits%20neatly%20into%20the%20company's%20brand%20strategy%2C%20she%20said%2C%20which%20is%20to%20evolve%20into%20more%20of%20a%20general%20gifting%20and%20value%20destination%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Btreasure%20hunt%26quot%3B%20and%20items%20you%20won't%20find%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20not%20just%20looking%20for%20big%20brands%20anymore%2C%20they're%20looking%20for%20hard-to-find%20niche%20things%20where%20they%20are%20literally%20the%20biggest%20client%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20things%20that%20makes%20them%20unique%20is%20they%20have%20buyers%20in%2012%20different%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20Sherman%20continued%2C%20adding%20that%20T.J.%20Maxx%20sources%20many%20of%20its%20products%20from%20small%20European%20vendors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20buyers%20in%20Spain%20who%20can%20find%20a%20set%20of%20little%20Spanish%20olives%20that%20they%20can%20then%20export%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFiona%20Fitzpatrick%2C%20a%20consumer%20packaged%20goods%20consultant%20who%20hosts%20the%20podcast%20%26quot%3BBrand%20Growth%20Heroes%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20BI%20that%20shoppers%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bdifferent%20pot%20of%20money%26quot%3B%20in%20their%20mind%20for%20buying%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20T.K.%20Maxx%2C%20the%20British%20arm%20of%20the%20company%2C%20F