ling%20to%20voice%20it.%20He'll%20only%20adopt%20a%20stance%20if%20it%20meets%20three%20criteria%3A%20it's%20important%2C%20has%20a%20good%20chance%20of%20happening%2C%20and%20is%20not%20yet%20a%20consensus%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20finds%20something%20that%20fulfills%20all%20three%20requirements%2C%20%26quot%3Bboy%2C%20you%20jump%20on%20them%20with%20all%20fours.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShilling%20gave%20the%20example%20of%20his%20accurate%20prediction%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bbond%20rally%20of%20a%20lifetime%26quot%3B%20in%201981.%20He%20was%20also%20one%20of%20only%20a%20few%20people%20including%20Burry%20to%20diagnose%20the%20mid-2000s%20housing%20bubble.%20Shilling%20partnered%20with%20hedge%20fund%20manager%20John%20Paulson%20to%20bet%20on%20a%20crash%2C%20and%20made%20about%2016%20times%20his%20money%20as%20a%20result%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAlways%20challenging%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20veteran%20economist%20might%20zig%20when%20others%20zag%2C%20but%20he%20doesn't%20consider%20himself%20a%20contrarian%20as%20he%20doesn't%20always%20disagree%20with%20the%20consensus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShilling%20said%20he%20was%20naturally%20inclined%20to%20probe%20the%20prevailing%20wisdom%20and%20interrogate%20others'%20claims%2C%20and%20his%20education%20honed%20that%20instinct.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20trained%20as%20a%20physicist%20%E2%80%94%20you%20always%20are%20challenging%2C%20always%20are%20looking%20for%20what's%20new%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20what's%20caused%20progress%20in%20the%20sciences%2C%20going%20back%20to%20Newton%20and%20Copernicus.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShilling%20said%20he%20finds%20taking%20a%20different%20view%20to%20be%20more%20intellectually%20stimulating%20than%20nodding%20along%20with%20the%20crowd.%20But%20he%20admitted%20it%20can%20be%20tough%20to%20disagree%20with%20the%20masses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20never-ending%20source%20of%20embarrassment%20for%20my%20wife%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20joked.%20Shilling%20explained%20that%20when%20the%20pair%20are%20guests%20at%20a%20cocktail%20party%2C%20someone%20might%20make%20an%20innocuous%20comment%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BIsn't%20that%20a%20beautiful%20yellow%20moon%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20can't%20resist%20replying%2C%20%26quot%3BAre%20you%20sure%20it%20isn't%20blue%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20market%20veterans%20have%20faced%20similar%20peer%20pressure%20to%20conform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%20In%20a%20recent%20memo%2C%20economist%20David%20Rosenberg%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavid-rosenberg-recession-forecast-prediction-contrarian-pushback-economy-growth-outlook-2023-8%3Futm_medium%3Dreferral%26utm_source%3Dyahoo.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edescribed%3C%2Fa%3E%20being%20mocked%2C%20yelled%20at%2C%20threatened%2C%20having%20things%20thrown%20at%20him%2C%20and%20being%20labeled%20the%20%26quot%3Bskunk%20at%20the%20picnic%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bclass%20clown%26quot%3B%20for%20predicting%20the%20mid-2000s%20housing%20bubble%20would%20end%20with%20a%20recession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShilling%20may%20not%20be%20facing%20quite%20that%20level%20of%20blowback%2C%20but%20it's%20certainly%20not%20easy%20to%20have%20conviction%20in%20one's%20contrarian%20views%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20they%20are%20more%20valuable%20to%20the%20market%20conversation%2C%20lucrative%2C%20and%20interesting%20to%20hold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgary-shilling-stock-market-crash-recession-contrarian-forecast-predictions-economy-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707653041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3b9dd43bb77284ba47a49%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgary-shilling-stock-market-crash-recession-contrarian-forecast-predictions-economy-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gary%20S