C%20as%20a%20rapturous%20crowd%20raising%20the%20Salai%20Taret%20flag%20cheered%20them%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stage-managed%20histrionics%20of%20it%20all%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20underestimated.%20The%20%E2%80%9Coath%E2%80%9D%20ceremony%20and%20Arambai%E2%80%99s%20triumphant%20parade%20afterwards%20marked%20the%20emergence%20of%20a%20new%20social%20contract%20in%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20one%20that%20allows%20an%20extrajudicial%20entity%20to%20claim%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20constitutional%20legitimacy%20and%20monopoly%20over%20violence.%20Even%20%E2%80%9CHobbessian%20anarchy%E2%80%9D%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20fully%20describe%20this%20dissolution%20of%20state%20power%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20Arambai%20administered%20the%20oath%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Sanamahi%2C%20a%20Meitei%20deity%2C%20lending%20the%20whole%20event%20a%20ethno-religious%20flavour.%20The%20demands%20included%20the%20removal%20of%20%E2%80%9CKuki%20illegal%20immigrants%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20(ST)%20list%20and%20conducting%20an%20Assam-like%20exercise%20to%20create%20a%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%20for%20Manipur%20with%201951%20as%20the%20base%20year.%20Both%20flow%20from%20the%20mischaracterisation%20by%20the%20Metei%20political%20elite%20and%20civil%20society%20of%20the%20Hills-based%20tribal%20community%20as%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20immigrants%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cinterlopers%E2%80%9D%20from%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-violence-reasons-failure-and-solution-q-and-a%5C%22%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20Behind%20the%20Manipur%20Violence%20and%20Why%20Stopping%20It%20Poses%20a%20Test%20for%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20challenge%20to%20state%20authority%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20summoning%20elected%20constitutional%20functionaries%20and%20forcing%20them%20to%20abandon%20their%20sworn%20oath%20of%20office%20to%20uphold%20the%20Indian%20constitution%2C%20while%20coercing%20them%20to%20take%20an%20ethno-political%20pledge%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20an%20affront%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20national%20security%20and%20political%20integrity%2C%20then%20what%20is%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%2C%20what%20is%20even%20more%20striking%20is%20that%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20is%20directly%20and%20morally%20implicated%20in%20this%20extra-constitutional%20event%20as%20a%20Union%20minister%20%E2%80%93%20Rajkumar%20Ranjan%20Singh%2C%20the%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20External%20Affairs%20%E2%80%93%20was%20also%20amongst%20the%20functionaries%20who%20took%20the%20oath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20by%20the%20logic%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20anti-terror%20law%2C%20Arambai%E2%80%99s%20actions%20from%20May%203%20onwards%20(and%2C%20specifically%20the%20January%2024%20event)%20amount%20to%20%E2%80%9Cterrorist%20act(s)%E2%80%9D%20and%20a%20threat%20to%20national%20security.%20Their%20actions%20fall%20squarely%20within%20the%20four%20corners%20of%20what%20is%20punishable%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20Prevention%20Act%20(UAPA)%2C%201967.%20They%20were%20undertaken%2C%20among%20others%2C%20with%20the%20%E2%80%9Cintent%20to%20strike%20terror%20in%20the%20people%E2%80%9D%20and%20to%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6compel%20the%20State%20Government%20or%20the%20Government%20of%20India%E2%80%9D%20to%20fulfil%20their%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Arambai%20is%20yet%20to%20face%20the%20music%20from%20the%20state.%20Let%20alone%20legal%20action%2C%20the%20Manipur%20police%20has%20not%20detained%20a%20single%20member%20of%20the%20armed%20group%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Coath-taking%E2%80%9D%20ceremony%20and%20the%20alleged%20violence%20against%20elected%20lawmakers.%20Neither%20has%20the%20state%20government%2C%20led%20by%20the%20BJP%20chief%20minister%2C%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20condemned%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-a-land-of-settled-grief%5C%22%3EManipur%3A%20A%20Land%20of%20Settled%20Grief%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Robinhood%20militia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20few%20months%2C%20Imphal%20and%20New%20Delhi%20have%20watched%20from%20the%20wings%20as%20Arambai%2C%20which%20had%20relatively%20lesser%20influence%20in%20Manipur%20before%20May%2C%20steadily%20grew%20in%20scope%20and%20size%20while%20chipping%20away%20at%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20authority%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fimphal-heavy-firing-manipur-rifles-and-armed-mob%5C%22%3Elooting%20arms%20from%20police%20armouries%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatodayne.in%2Fmanipur%2Fstory%2Fgunfight-erupts-between-arambai-tenggol-militants-and-37-assam-rifles-in-manipur-567375-2023-05-30%5C%22%3Eattacking%20central%20forces%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJamangKuki%2Fstatus%2F1721167803989025180%2Fvideo%2F1%5C%22%3Ebrandishing%20weapons%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20public%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20militias%20is%20a%20complex%20phenomenon%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20context%20of%20an%20active%20multi-ethnic%20conflict.%20So%2C%20there%20may%20be%20many%20reasons%20why%20the%20Arambai%20managed%20to%20break%20through%20the%20glass%20wall%20of%20public%20opinion%20and%20become%20somewhat%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9CRobinhood%20militia%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20a%20clear%20factor%20behind%20its%20ascendance%20is%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20critical%20political%20vacuum%20in%20Meitei%20society%20since%20the%20conflict%20began%20in%20May.%20It%20is%20likely%20that%20large%20sections%20of%20the%20population%20no%20longer%20trust%20the%20Singh%20government%20to%20protect%20their%20interests.%20Arambai%20emerged%20as%20a%20more%20viable%20and%20compelling%20alternative%2C%20not%20least%20because%20of%20its%20resolute%20military%20action%20at%20the%20frontlines.%20Despite%20growing%20evidence%20of%20their%20role%20in%20perpetuating%20violence%20against%20the%20Kuki-Zomis%2C%20an%20editor%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3EPeople%E2%80%99s%20Chronicle%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20an%20Imphal-based%20publication%2C%20had%20called%20the%20militia%E2%80%99s%20role%20and%20influence%20in%20Manipur%20since%20May%20as%20being%20akin%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%2F2023%2F06%2F09%2Fa-pen-can-do-more-harm-than-a-gun-in-manipur-meitei-owned-media-is-winning-the-perception-war%5C%22%3EWhatsApp%20group%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Meitei%20public%20now%20sees%20the%20Arambai%20as%20a%20unifying%20political%20force%2C%20rather%20than%20just%20their%20rightful%20military%20representative.%20For%20them%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Coath-taking%E2%80%9D%20ceremony%20was%20the%20group%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20to%20discipline%20Meitei%20lawmakers%20across%20the%20political%20spectrum%20and%20compel%20them%20to%20uphold%20core%20concerns%20of%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20Kangla%20Fort%20event%2C%20with%20all%20its%20spectacular%20symbolism%20and%20political%20iconography%2C%20has%20thickened%20the%20air%20of%20myth%20and%20enigma%20around%20Arambai%20Tenggol%2C%20a%20name%20that%20evocatively%20refers%20to%20the%20dart-wielding%20calvary%20force%20of%20the%20ancient%20Meitei%20kingdom%20of%20Kangleipak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBroad%20appeal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20Arambai%20seems%20to%20have%20become%20even%20more%20popular%20than%20the%20established%20(and%20proscribed)%20Meitei%20armed%20groups%2C%20such%20as%20the%20United%20National%20Liberation%20Front%20(UNLF)%2C%20People%E2%80%99s%20Liberation%20Army%20(PLA)%2C%20and%20Kanglei%20Yawol%20Kanna%20Lup%20(KYKL).%20It%20seems%20to%20have%20been%20more%20successful%20than%20these%20older%20insurgent%20groups%20in%20drawing%20the%20disenchanted%20and%20disgruntled%20Meitei%20youth%20into%20a%20programme%20of%20patriotism%20and%20direct%20action.%20In%20fact%2C%20even%20in%20terms%20of%20actual%20armed%20action%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20the%20Arambai%20appear%20to%20have%20overshadowed%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20older%20groups%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20potential%20turf%20war%20between%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20more%20worrying%20perhaps%20is%20that%20the%20Arambai%E2%80%99s%20soaring%20influence%20among%20the%20Meiteis%2C%20including%20their%20public%20figures%2C%20will%20further%20discourage%20the%20Biren%20Singh%20government%20from%20acting%20against%20it.%20By%20moving%20against%20the%20group%2C%20Biren%20Singh%20could%20alienate%20his%20core%20constituencies%20and%20thus%2C%20make%20himself%20less%20politically%20valuable%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20high%20command.%20This%20creates%20a%20fatal%20deadlock%2C%20which%20allows%20the%20Arambai%20to%20not%20just%20persist%2C%20but%20also%20grow%20even%20bigger%20and%20stronger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20recent%20past%2C%20prominent%20Meitei%20personalities%2C%20such%20as%20Bollywood%20actress%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC2h1D58tWMo%2F%3Figsh%3DMXR3d3AxMWRyeXp1eg%3D%3D%5C%22%3ELin%20Laishram%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Licypriya%20Kangujam%2C%20a%2012-year-old%20climate%20activist%2C%20have%20publicly%20expressed%20their%20support%20for%20the%20Arambai%20on%20social%20media.%20Licypriya%20had%20even%20mobilised%20funds%20for%20the%20purchase%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthefrontiermanipur.com%2Fchild-activist-licypriya-hands-over-thermal-drones-items-to-at%2F%5C%22%3Ethermal%20imaging%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20militia%20to%20use%20in%20their%20fight%20against%20what%20she%20called%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20Kuki%20Narco%20Terrorist%E2%80%9D.%20Using%20social%20service%20acts%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fksherson.thoudam%2Fposts%2Fpfbid02dx7VHC69FmiAkXpsWxuUeYz8uFihf6yqME9fij8mzq8qaVkqYDThaSqyneCBhZfMl%5C%22%3Edistributing%20aid%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Meitei%20relief%20camps%2C%20the%20Arambai%20has%20been%20able%20to%20command%20wide%20appeal%20in%20Meitei%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECollusion%20with%20state%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVarious%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-more-than-five-dead-dozens-injured-over-the-last-two-weeks-amid-ongoing-ethnic-unrest%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20mainstream%20and%20social%20media%20have%20indicated%20that%20the%20Arambai%20enjoys%20high-profile%20patronage%20from%20the%20Meitei%20ruling%20elite.%20Even%20before%20the%20conflict%20began%20in%20May%2C%20it%20had%20the%20attention%20of%20senior%20political%20figures.%20Pictures%20from%20August%202022%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Farambai-tenggol-group-manipur-meitei-mla-9128683%2F%5C%22%3Eshow%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20militia%E2%80%99s%20leader%2C%20Khuman%2C%20sitting%20with%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20Leishemba%20Sanajaoba%2C%20the%20titular%20king%20of%20Manipur%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP.%20A%20Facebook%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHHSanajaoba.Leishemba%2Fvideos%2Foath-taking-ceremony-of-arambai-tenggol-group-at-my-residence250922%2F430995689136627%2F%5C%22%3Evideo%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20September%20that%20year%20shows%20cadres%20taking%20some%20kind%20of%20oath%20at%20Sanajaoba%E2%80%99s%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20the%20Kuki-Zomi%20community%20have%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1050361%2Farmed-gangs-and-a-partisan-state-how-manipur-slipped-into-civil-war%5C%22%3Eaccused%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20state%20police%20of%20providing%20cover%20to%20Arambai%20cadres%20during%20violent%20attacks%20against%20their%20villages.%20Kuki-Zomi%20organisations%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fmanipur%2Fsecurity-forces-struggle-to-recover-snatched-weapons-in-conflict-hit-manipur-2656856%5C%22%3Eaccused%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20police%20of%20handing%20over%20arms%20to%20Arambai%20members%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20have%20openly%20flaunted%20them%20in%20public.%20This%20marks%20a%20sinister%20blurring%20of%20lines%20between%20state%20and%20non-state%20armed%20actors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20why%20has%20this%20happened%3F%20One%20reason%20could%20be%20that%20the%20Manipur%20government%20was%20keen%20on%20delegating%20the%20mandate%20of%20law%20enforcement%20to%20other%20actors.%20But%2C%20there%20may%20be%20other%20factors%20in%20an%20ethnically%20loaded%20context.%20Writing%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F24546330%3Fseq%3D1%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EJournal%20of%20Conflict%20Resolution%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Sabine%20C.%20Carey%2C%20Michael%20P.%20Colaresi%20and%20Neil%20J.%20Mitchell%20argue%20that%20%E2%80%9Cgovernments%20perceive%20ties%20to%20militias%20as%20a%20mechanism%20to%20evade%20accountability%20and%20muddy%20the%20flow%20of%20information%20about%20who%20is%20responsible%20for%20violence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20is%20reminded%20of%20the%20Arab%20Janjaweed%20militia%20in%20Sudan%2C%20which%2C%20supported%20by%20the%20government%2C%20wreaked%20havoc%20in%20the%20Darfur%20region%20two%20decades%20ago.%20It%20showed%20the%20world%20the%20catastrophic%20consequences%20of%20a%20government%20giving%20%3Cem%3Ecarte%20blanche%3C%2Fem%3E%20(and%20access%20to%20small%20arms)%20to%20an%20ethnic%20militia.%20The%20example%20of%20Libya%20after%202011%20also%20comes%20to%20mind.%20The%20vacuum%20that%20the%20killing%20of%20Muammar%20al-Qaddafi%20by%20NATO-linked%20forces%20left%20was%20quickly%20filled%20up%20by%20various%20militias%2C%20which%20then%20went%20on%20to%20claim%20state%20authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20one%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20go%20that%20far.%20Right%20next%20to%20Manipur%2C%20the%20Myanmar%20military%20has%20been%20using%20a%20violent%20militia%20known%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprogressivevoicemyanmar.org%2F2022%2F03%2F12%2Fthe-rising-of-pyu-saw-htee%2F%5C%22%3EPyu%20Saw%20Htee%20(PSH)%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20fight%20its%20dirty%20war%20against%20pro-democracy%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-violence-claims-counterclaims-meitei-kuki%5C%22%3EDispelling%20Some%20Misleading%20Claims%20About%20the%20Violence%20in%20Manipur%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArambai%E2%80%99s%20growing%20political%20shadow%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20demands%20that%20Arambai%20had%20made%20in%20its%20%E2%80%9Cresolution%E2%80%9D%20during%20the%20Kangla%20event%20was%20fencing%20the%20India-Myanmar%20border.%20It%20had%20given%20New%20Delhi%2015%20days%20to%20fulfil%20the%20demand.%20On%20February%203%2C%20Singh%20travelled%20to%20New%20Delhi%20to%20meet%20Shah%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNBirenSingh%2Fstatus%2F1753733494499332544%5C%22%3Erevealed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20government%20was%20%E2%80%9Cset%20to%20take%20some%20important%20decisions%20in%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Manipur.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20days%20later%2C%20and%2012%20days%20after%20Arambai%20made%20its%20demands%2C%20Shah%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Findia-to-fence-indo-myanmar-border-says-amit-shah-work-underway-in-arunachal-pradesh-and-manipur-11707231157754.html%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20would%20fence%20the%20entire%20border.%20Two%20days%20later%2C%20he%20announced%20that%20the%20home%20ministry%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAmitShah%2Fstatus%2F1755482704152305786%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1755482704152305786%257Ctwgr%255E597147d62001f291c1d58d0a8285008a89cbd22c%257Ctwcon%255Es1_%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Findianexpress.com%252Farticle%252Findia%252Ffree-movement-regime-india-myanmar-amit-shah-9150557%252F%5C%22%3Esuspended%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Free%20Movement%20Regime%20(FMR)%20that%20allows%20visa-free%20travel%20along%20the%2016-kilometre%20band%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20wonders%20if%20these%20big-ticket%20decisions%20are%20directly%20linked%20to%20Arambai%E2%80%99s%20demands%20(and%20deadline).%20If%20so%2C%20it%20is%20a%20deeply%20worrying%20sign%20of%20New%20Delhi%20giving%20in%20to%20an%20anarchic%20power%20in%20Manipur.%20It%20is%20also%20a%20sign%20of%20Arambai%E2%80%99s%20political%20sway%20in%20not%20just%20Imphal%2C%20but%20far%20beyond%20it%2C%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20two%20days%20before%20the%20Kangla%20event%2C%20an%20official%20central%20delegation%20composed%20of%20the%20interlocutor%20for%20the%20Kuki-Zomi%20insurgent%20groups%2C%20%5Borganised%20under%20the%20United%20People%E2%80%99s%20Front%20(UPF)%20and%20the%20Kuki%20National%20Organization%20(KNO)%5D%2C%20A.K.%20Mishra%2C%20and%20two%20senior%20officials%20from%20the%20Intelligence%20Bureau%20(IB)%20were%20rushed%20to%20Imphal%20to%20hold%20a%20series%20of%20meetings%20with%20the%20Arambai.%20It%20is%20likely%20that%20they%20wanted%20to%20reach%20a%20compromise%20to%20prevent%20a%20coup%20d%E2%80%99etat%20in%20Manipur.%20Clearly%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20too%2C%20can%E2%80%99t%20dismiss%2C%20let%20alone%20challenge%2C%20the%20militia%E2%80%99s%20influence%20in%20Imphal.%20In%20turn%2C%20Arambai%20is%20able%20to%20cement%20its%20credibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMerely%20two%20days%20after%20the%20Kangla%20Fort%20event%2C%20the%20state%20government%20hosted%20Republic%20Day%20at%20the%20same%20location.%20In%20his%20speech%2C%20Singh%20paid%20homage%20to%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20and%20urged%20the%20people%20to%20%E2%80%9Crespect%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20and%20one%20another%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D.%E2