%2Fwhich-trader-joes-sausages-to-buy-ranking-review-photos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epork%20sausages%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20a%20good%20meat%20content%20(56%25%20pork)%20for%20the%20price%20(about%20%244).%20They're%20subtly%20flavored%20with%20white%20pepper%20and%20a%20few%20herbs%2C%20which%20makes%20them%20very%20versatile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20found%20that%20these%20sausages%20are%20as%20good%20on%20a%20sandwich%20as%20they%20are%20in%20a%20chili.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20all%20the%20methods%20I%20used%2C%20the%20packaging%20only%20included%20instructions%20for%20pan-frying%2C%20so%20I%20searched%20online%20for%20recommendations%20for%20the%20other%20times%20and%20cooking%20temperatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20started%20with%20the%20stove%20since%20I%20knew%20it%20would%20take%20the%20longest.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223331%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22four%20sausage%20links%20cooking%20in%20a%20pan%20on%20the%20stove%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3a98643bb77284ba46ba6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222498%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20induction%20stove%20can%20get%20pretty%20hot%2C%20so%20I%20started%20at%20medium-low%20heat.%20%3Cp%3EAndy%20Lynes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20instructions%20on%20the%20packaging%20said%20to%20preheat%20a%20teaspoon%20of%20oil%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-copper-cookware%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efrying%20pan%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20medium%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20an%20induction%20stove%2C%20so%20I%20went%20with%20a%20medium-low%20setting%20to%20prevent%20the%20skins%20from%20catching%20or%20burning%20before%20the%20sausages%20were%20ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20added%20them%20to%20the%20pan%20after%20about%2030%20seconds%20and%20turned%20the%20links%20every%20two%20minutes%20or%20so%20using%20tongs%20to%20ensure%20even%20browning.%20I%20also%20rested%20th