ed%20my%20air%20fryer%20for%20five%20minutes%20at%20390%20degrees%20Fahrenheit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20recipe%20I%20found%20said%20it%20wasn't%20necessary%20to%20use%20oil%2C%20based%20on%20previous%20experiences%20cooking%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fair-fryer-steak%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emeats%20in%20the%20air%20fryer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20tossed%20the%20sausages%20in%20a%20teaspoon%20of%20oil%20to%20encourage%20browning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ensured%20the%20sausages%20were%20spread%20out%20in%20the%20basket%20so%20they'd%20cook%20and%20brown%20evenly%20and%20set%20the%20cooking%20time%20to%2015%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20five%20minutes%2C%20I%20turned%20the%20sausages%20using%20tongs.%20I%20checked%20again%20after%2010%20more%20minutes%2C%20and%20they%20were%20completely%20cooked%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAir%20frying%20took%20nearly%20half%20the%20time%2C%20but%20the%20results%20were%20disappointing.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22four%20cooked%20sausage%20links%20in%20an%20air%20fryer%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3a9d77a3d271488788701%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20sausages%20split%20and%20leaked%20in%20the%20air%20fryer.%20%3Cp%3EAndy%20Lynes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20cooking%2C%20the%20sausages%20split%20open%2C%20which%20meant%20a%20lot%20of%20fat%20leaked%20out%20and%20they%20weren't%20very%20juicy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20skins%20were%20unevenly%20cooked%20and%20had%20become%20a%20bit%20tough%20%E2%80%94%20the%20texture%20and%20appearance%20weren't%20nearly%20as%20appealing%20as%20the%20stove-cooked%20sausages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20might%20be%20possible%20to%20get%20a%20better%20result%20by%20tweaking%20the%20temperature%20and%20cooking%20times%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20love%20these.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%2