-no-data-return-to-office-rto-aws-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20admitted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20company's%20return-to-office%20mandate%20isn't%20based%20on%20data%20but%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bjudgment%26quot%3B%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225001%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Andy%20Jassy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F601ab6ac01504a00197fb59b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmazon%20chief%20executive%20Andy%20Jassy.%3Cp%3EMike%20Blake%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20November%2C%20Amazon%20also%20added%20a%20no-promotions%20policy%20for%20perennial%20remote%20workers.%20Unless%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethey%20come%20into%20the%20office%20three%20times%20a%20week%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethey%20don't%20qualify.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20email%20to%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBI%2C%20an%20Amazon%20representative%20said%20compliance%20with%20the%20RTO%20policy%20was%20one%20of%20the%20many%20factors%20it%20considers%20before%20an%20employee%20is%20promoted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20companies%20including%20Google%20and%20Ernst%20%26amp%3B%20Young%20(EY)%2C%20are%20introducing%20new%20ways%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-companies-spy-on-employees-bossware-jpmorgan-amazon-monitor-rto-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emonitor%20attendance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20using%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethat%20data%20in%20performance%20reviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECary%20Cooper%2C%20an%20organizational%20psychologist%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Manchester%20and%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BRemote%20Workplace%20Culture%2C%26quot%3B%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etold%20BI%20that%20the%20increased%20oversight%20is%20a%20symptom%20of%20antiquated%20management%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20dinosaur%20management%20of%20the%20highest%20order.%20They%20don't%20understand%20the