rded%20with%20some%20of%20the%20catches%20he%20took.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe'd%20discuss%20the%20position%20of%20his%20feet%2C%20the%20height%20he%20gets%2C%20where%20his%20hands%20are.%20He%20leads%20it.%20We%20used%20the%20Merlin%20spin%20machine%2C%20mats%20that%20spin%20or%20one%20with%20holes%20cut%20in%20them%2C%20so%20that%20some%20spin%20and%20some%20bounce.%20We%20do%20it%20from%2022%20yards%2C%20or%20from%20ten%20or%2011%20yards.%20He%20knows%20what%20he%20wants%20to%20work%20on%20and%20we've%20done%20that%20since%20he%20joined%20us%20in%202014%20from%20Essex.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20said%20a%20while%20ago%20he's%20the%20best%20in%20the%20world%20and%2C%20but%20for%20circumstances%2C%20he%20could%20be%20coming%20up%20to%20playing%2050%20or%2060%20Tests%2C%20but%20I%20get%20the%20need%20to%20balance%20the%20side%20and%20that's%20why%20he's%20not%20played%20(more).%20People%20should%20not%20underestimate%20his%20batting%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707649320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F187uu248_sac_625x300_11_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-england-2024%2Fms-dhoni-had-quick-hands-but-england-great-makes-sensational-claim-5037136%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alec%20Stewart%20was%20all%20praise%20for%20Ben%20Foakes%20and%20added%20that%20currently%2C%20he%20is%20faster%20behind%20the%20stumps%20in%20comparison%20to%20MS%20Dhoni.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22600%2B%20Writers%2C%20Poets%20Urge%20PEN%20America%20to%20Do%20the%20'Bare%20Minimum'%20for%20Palestinian%20Authors%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11160244%2FGF6cP-3WEAEJ033.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EMore%20than%20600%2