20the%20225%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flithub.com%2Fthese-are-the-poets-and-writers-who-have-been-killed-in-gaza%2F%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Flithub.com%2Fthese-are-the-poets-and-writers-who-have-been-killed-in-gaza%2F%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1707517222034000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3fLusKiCz5MruUOsL_ckLb%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epoets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20playwrights%2C%20journalists%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F1%2F24%2Fhow-israel-has-destroyed-gazas-schools-and-universities%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F1%2F24%2Fhow-israel-has-destroyed-gazas-schools-and-universities%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1707517222034000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3VKitr-iVk2G3_iaFWF86r%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escholars%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20novelists%20killed%20in%20Gaza%20and%20name%20their%20murderer%3A%20Israel%2C%20a%20Zionist%20colonial%20state%20funded%20by%20the%20U.S.%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EPEN%20International%20and%20its%20affiliate%2C%20PEN%20America%2C%20operate%20under%20the%20mission%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdefend%20writers%2C%20artists%2C%20and%20journalists%20and%20protect%20free%20expression.%E2%80%9D%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.democracynow.org%2F2024%2F1%2F17%2Fgaza_journalists_killed%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.democracynow.org%2F2024%2F1%2F17%2Fgaza_journalists_killed%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1707517222034000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3av7a2VExL2vGo0C_P4vJ8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20DemocracyNow%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CGaza%20is%20now%20the%20deadliest%20place%20on%20Earth%20for%20media%20workers.%E2%80%9D%20We%20demand%20PEN%20take%20significant%20steps%20to%20save%20lives.%20As%20this%20letter%20circulates%2C%20the%20death%20toll%20among%20Palestinian%20writers%20and%20reporters%20will%20likely%20grow.%20On%20October%2025th%20PEN%20International%20called%20for%20a%20ceasefire.%20Meanwhile%2C%20PEN%20America%20has%20remained%20silent%2C%20and%20it%20has%20become%20apparent%20to%20the%20public%20whose%20lives%20and%20voices%20matter%20to%20it%20and%20whose%20don%E2%80%99t.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EPEN%20America%20continually%20perpetuates%20fascist%20nation-statehood%2C%20which%20becomes%20especially%20dangerous%20when%20the%20organization%20is%20so%20keen%20to%20define%20literary%20citizenship%20and%20freedom%20of%20speech.%20Whose%20freedom%20does%20PEN%20protect%2C%20if%20outside%20of%20press%20releases%20buried%20on%20its%20website%2C%20PEN%20has%20remained%20silent%20about%20Palestinian%20journalists%2C%20writers%2C%20and%20poets%20murdered%20by%20Israel%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EOn%20January%2031%2C%20PEN%20America%20chose%20to%20platform%20Mayim%20Bialik%2C%20a%20person%20committed%20to%20the%20racist%20ideology%20of%20Zionism.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20PEN%20is%20perpetuating%20dangerous%2C%20fascist%20views%20and%20offering%20tacit%20approval%20for%20the%20Zionist%2C%20racist%20and%20genocidal%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EPEN%20Members%20and%20representatives%20from%20Writers%20Against%20the%20War%20On%20Gaza%20(WAWOG)%20protested%20this%20event%20indoors.%20Among%20them%20was%20Randa%20Jarrar%2C%20a%20Palestinian%20writer%20who%20has%20done%20weeks%20of%20unpaid%20labor%20for%20PEN%20as%20an%20event%20host%2C%20organizer%2C%20and%20judge%20of%20PEN%E2%80%99s%20Open%20Book%20prize%20and%20Robert%20Bingham%20prize.%20Rather%20than%20defending%20Jarrar%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20free%20expression%2C%20PEN%20America%20violently%20dragged%20her%20out%20of%20the%20event%20by%20her%20audience%20chair%2C%20and%20threatened%20her%20with%20state%20violence%2C%20stating%20that%20if%20she%20did%20not%20silence%20herself%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20Police%20Department%20would%20be%20summoned%20to%20silence%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWe%20demand%20that%20PEN%20America%20apologize%20to%20Jarrar%20for%20these%20actions%20and%20take%20more%20concrete%20steps%20to%20support%20Palestinian%20writers%20in%20the%20face%20of%20a%20new%20wave%20of%20repression%2C%20retaliation%20and%20bigotry%20rippling%20through%20publishing%2C%20academia%2C%20and%20the%20creative%20arts%20industries.%20We%20demand%20PEN%20America%20create%20a%20legal%20strategy%20to%20get%20Palestinian%20authors%20and%20poets%20asylum%20immediately%2C%20and%20to%20publicize%20these%20efforts%3B%20to%20use%20its%20institutional%20power%20and%20resources%2C%20just%20as%20PEN%20does%20under%20the%20Writers%20in%20Crisis%20and%20Writers%20at%20Risk%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWe%20demand%20PEN%20raise%20just%20as%20much%20hell%20over%20the%20unlawful%20detainment%20since%20December%2012%20of%20Mostafa%20Sheta%2C%20director%20of%20the%20Freedom%20Theater%20in%20Jenin%2C%20by%20Zionist%20occupation%20forces%2C%20as%20they%20do%20about%20those%20being%20unlawfully%20detained%20by%20states%20in%20opposition%20to%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWe%20demand%20PEN%20find%20the%20same%20zeal%20and%20passion%20that%20they%20have%20for%20banned%20books%20in%20the%20US%20to%20speak%20out%20about%20actual%20human%20beings%20in%20Palestine.%20As%20PEN%20America%20advances%20its%20campaigns%20against%20book%20banning%20and%20freedom%20of%20speech%20on%20campuses%20throughout%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20Zionist%20occupation%20forces%20have%20damaged%20or%20destroyed%20372%20educational%20facilities%2C%20including%20every%20single%20university%20and%20the%20Gaza%20Municipal%20Library%2C%20which%20ser