%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107600891.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EMithun%20Chakraborty%2C%20a%20veteran%20actor%20and%20politician%2C%20suffered%20an%20Ischemic%20Cerebrovascular%20Stroke%20but%20is%20now%20feeling%20better.%20Known%20for%20films%20like%20'Disco%20Dancer'%20and%20'Mard%2C'%20he%20was%20rushed%20to%20a%20private%20hospital%20in%20Kolkata%20and%20is%20currently%20recovering.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pak%20Ultra-Right%20Party%20Infamous%20For%20Anti-Blasphemy%20Protests%20Slips%20In%20Polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20leader%20of%20an%20ultra-right%20Pakistan%20party%20infamous%20for%20sometimes%20bloody%20anti-blasphemy%20agitation%20has%20vowed%20a%20comeback%20after%20its%20vote%20share%20evaporated%20in%20elections%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBlasphemy%20is%20a%20charged%20topic%20in%20Muslim-majority%20Pakistan%20where%20the%20faintest%20whisper%20of%20a%20slight%20toward%20the%20Prophet%20Muhammad%20can%20embolden%20lynch%20mobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaad%20Hussain%20Rizvi's%20Tehreek-e-Labbaik%20Pakistan%20(TLP)%20party%20rode%20the%20issue%20to%20emerge%20as%20the%20largest%20Islamist%20force%20in%202018%20polls%2C%20but%20its%20prominence%20was%20all%20but%20eroded%20in%20last%20week's%20national%20and%20provincial%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20say%20the%20death%20of%20Rizvi's%20charismatic%20father%2C%20who%20founded%20the%20party%2C%20and%20a%20loss%20of%20patronage%20from%20Pakistan's%20powerful%20generals%20cost%20them%20dearly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20supporters%20in%20the%20centre%20of%20cultural%20capital%20Lahore%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Rizvi%20said%20the%20enemies%20of%20Islam%20had%20stopped%20his%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20rigging%20has%20taken%20place%20because%20we%20speak%20about%20rights%2C%20and%20we%20talk%20about%20a%20faith%20that%20those%20with%20power%20in%20this%20world%20do%20not%20accept%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20he%20could%20fill%20his%20father%20Khadim%20Hussain%20Rizvi's%20shoes%2C%20he%20responded%20matter-of-factly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBringing%20people%20onto%20the%20streets%2C%20and%20bringing%20people%20out%20to%20vote%20was%20not%20a%20problem%20for%20TLP%20in%20the%20past%20and%20it%20is%20not%20a%20problem%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crowd%20of%202%2C000%20people%20there%20to%20hear%20him%20speak%20--%20though%20enthusiastic%20--%20was%20a%20far%20cry%20from%20the%20tens%20of%20thousands%20that%20used%20to%20hang%20on%20to%20his%20father's%20every%20word.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKhadim%20Rizvi%20had%20the%20kind%20of%20leadership%20and%20charisma%20that%20his%20son%20does%20not%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20Arafat%20Mazhar%2C%20who%20works%20on%20blasphemy%20law%20reform%2C%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20religion%20had%20dropped%20down%20the%20pecking%20order%20in%20elections%20defined%20by%20%26quot%3Banti-establishment%20politics%26quot%3B%2C%20as%20Pakistan%20battles%20a%20massive%20economic%20crisis%20and%20an%20erosion%20of%20trust%20in%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BWe%20Have%20God%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETLP%20has%20its%20ideological%20roots%20in%20Barelvi%20Islam%20--%20a%20mainstream%20sect%20traditionally%20seen%20as%20moderate%20but%20for%20which%20blasphemy%20is%20a%20red%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20first%20began%20making%20waves%20in%202016%2C%20when%20protesting%20the%20execution%20of%20Mumtaz%20Qadri%2C%20a%20bodyguard%20who%20assassinated%20the%20governor%20of%20Punjab%20province%20over%20his%20stance%20on%20blasphemy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20say%20its%20street%20power%20was%20tapped%20by%20the%20military%20a%20year%20later%20to%20reduce%20the%20voter%20base%20of%20Nawaz%20Sharif's%20centre-right%20party%2C%20which%20had%20fallen%20foul%20of%20the%20generals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20suspicions%20at%20the%20time%20that%20certain%20elements%20within%20intelligence%20agencies%20were%20encouraging%20them%20to%20destabilise%20the%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20public%20policy%20analyst%20Ahmed%20Bilal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20element%20may%20no%20longer%20be%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20went%20rogue%20following%20its%20electoral%20success%2C%20orchestrating%20violent%20anti-Sweden%20and%20anti-France%20protests%20after%20incidents%20of%20Koran%20burning%20and%20satirical%20cartoons%20of%20the%20Prophet%20Mohammed%20in%20those%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20years%20on%2C%20Sharif%20is%20back%20in%20favour%20and%20his%20successor%20Imran%20Khan%20in%20jail%20in%20the%20see-saw%20world%20of%20Pakistan%20politics%20--%20reducing%20TLP's%20utility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20years%20ago%20TLP%20bagged%20more%20than%20two%20million%20votes%20to%20become%20the%20fifth-largest%20party%20in%20the%20country%20--%20ahead%20of%20more%20established%20Islamist%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThursday's%20polls%20were%20less%20successful%20for%20all%20of%20Pakistan's%20religious%20parties%2C%20however%2C%20leading%20Rizvi%20to%20call%20on%20supporters%20to%20come%20out%20and%20protest%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20party%20had%20been%20tipped%20to%20gain%20more%20electoral%20seats%2C%20but%20Mazhar%20said%20its%20appeal%20only%20exists%20in%20times%20of%20perceived%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20there%20is%20not%20an%20imagined%20threat%20around%20the%20prophet%20or%20religion%20in%20the%20country%20then%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20governance%20people%20don't%20want%20them%20in%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20only%20through%20anxiety-inducing%20politics%20that%20they%20can%20get%20votes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERizvi%20insists%20they%20will%20be%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20atop%20a%20makeshift%20stage%20on%20the%20back%20of%20a%20truck%2C%20he%20proclaimed%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20the%20power%2C%20we%20have%20God.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707647580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F3tkkflpo_saad-hussain-rizvi_625x300_11_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpak-ultra-right-party-tehreek-e-labbaik-pakistan-infamous-for-anti-blasphemy-protests-slips-in-polls-5037046%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20leader%20of%20an%20ultra-right%20Pakistan%20party%20infamous%20for%20sometimes%20bloody%20anti-blasphemy%20agitation%20has%20vowed%20a%20comeback%20after%20its%20vote%20share%20evaporated%20in%20elections%20last%20week.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpak-ultra-right-party-tehreek-e-labbaik-pakistan-infamous-for-anti-blasphemy-protests-slips-in-polls-5037046%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpak-ultra-right-party-tehreek-e-labbaik-pakistan-infamous-for-anti-blasphemy-protests-slips-in-polls-5037046%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpak-ultra-right-party-tehreek-e-labbaik-pakistan-infamous-for-anti-blasphemy-protests-slips-in-polls-5037046%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Even%20opposition%20leaders%20saying%20'abki%20baar%20400%20paar'%3A%20PM%20Modi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707647577000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107600911%2Cimgsize-1178856.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Feven-opposition-leaders-saying-abki-baar-400-paar-pm-modi-in-mp%2Farticleshow%2F107600064.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20while%20addressing%20a%20rally%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20on%20Sunday%2C%20stated%20that%20even%20opposition%20leaders%20are%20now%20saying%20%26quot%3Babki%20baar%20400%20paar%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20the%20BJP's%20main%20campaign%20theme%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20PM%20Modi%20highlighted%20that%20even%20in%20Parliament%2C%20opposition%20leaders%20are%20now%20expressing%20support%20for%20the%20NDA%20by%20using%20the%20same%20phrase.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Talking%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F07131439%2FIMG_0107-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9COn%20principle%20it%20is%20quite%20wrong%20to%20try%20founding%20a%20theory%20on%20observable%20magnitude%20alone.%20In%20reality%20the%20very%20opposite%20happens.%20It%20is%20the%20theory%20which%20decides%20what%20we%20can%20observe.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%88%BC%20Albert%20Einstein%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%205%2C%202024%2C%20chief%20minister%20of%20Uttarakhand%20Pushkar%20Singh%20Dhami%20tabled%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20(UCC)%20Bill%20.%20The%20rather%20complex%20document%20(with%20seven%20schedules%20and%20392%20sections)%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20House%20the%20very%20next%20day.%20Uttarakhand%20thus%20becomes%20the%20first%20state%20in%20independent%20India%20to%20pass%20a%20common%20law%20on%20marriage%2C%20divorce%2C%20inheritance%20and%20even%20live-in%20relationships%20between%20two%20consenting%20adults.%20The%20hurry%20with%20which%20the%20Bill%20was%20brought%20and%20passed%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%202024%20elections%20clearly%20indicates%20a%20similar%20passage%20for%20the%20Bill%20in%20all%20other%20states%2C%20should%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20win%20with%20a%20large%20majority%2C%20of%20which%20they%20seem%20very%20sure.%20And%20when%20that%20is%20done%20we%20will%20have%20a%20pan-Indian%20civil%20society%20the%20BJP%20wishes%20to%20build.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20293px)%2085vw%2C%20293px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mrinal%20Pande%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22293%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%20525w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783-246x300.jpg%20246w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-642789%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22357%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20swiftly%20released%20press%20note%20from%20a%20group%20of%20Uttarakhandi%20women%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20contents%20of%20the%20Bill%20became%20public%2C%20the%20women%20of%20Uttarakhand%20had%20protested%20and%20rejected%20the%20draft%20in%20toto.%20According%20to%20the%20note%20which%20seems%20to%20have%20been%20disregarded%2C%20the%20Bill%20was%20built%20along%20the%20patriarchal%20Hindu%20law%20template%20and%20retained%20several%20discriminatory%20aspects%20that%20would%20deny%20women%20an%20equal%20agency%20.%20The%20leaders%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community%20have%20also%20protested%20over%20the%20UCC%20overtaking%20Muslim%20personal%20laws.%20The%20new%20law%20lacks%20clarity%20for%20both%20groups%20and%20that%20may%20cause%20heavy%20snarls%20when%20it%20is%20implemented.%20It%20does%20not%2C%20for%20example%2C%20distinguish%20between%20ancestral%20or%20self-acquired%20property.%20It%20seems%20to%20promote%20intrusive%20moral%20policing%20and%20may%20result%20in%C2%A0%20discriminatory%20harassment%20of%20adults%20in%20a%20relationship%20that%20has%20been%20considered%20autonomous%20and%20consensual.%20Some%20of%20the%20rules%20may%20become%20clearer%20when%20gazetted%20but%20the%20compulsory%20registration%20of%20live-in%20relationships%20is%20full%20of%20explosive%20landmines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202005%2C%20when%20the%20Hindu%20Succession%20(Amendment)%20Act%20was%20passed%20thus%20giving%20daughters%20equal%20coparcenary%20rights%20in%20ancestral%20property%2C%20the%20then%20law%20minister%20was%20asked%20by%20the%20distinguished%20lawyer%20Fali%20Nariman%20whether%20his%20government%20would%20follow%20this%20with%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20binding%20on%20all%20Indians.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%E2%80%99t%20speak%20for%20all%20communities%20unless%20they%20are%20ready.%E2%80%9D%20This%20care%20for%20the%20sentiments%20and%20reservations%20among%20the%20actual%20stakeholders%20was%20mostly%20lacking%20in%20the%20preparation%20and%20the%20hasty%20passage%20of%20the%20UCC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20grassroots%20reality%2C%20was%20even%20the%20Hindu%20community%20of%20Uttarakhand%20prepped%20and%20well%20informed%20about%20the%20various%20provisions%20of%20the%20new%20law%3F%20Does%20it%20know%20that%20the%201.89%25%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20population%20has%20been%20kept%20out%20of%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20Bill%2C%20and%20has%20(according%20to%20a%20report%20based%20on%20the%20NFHS%20survey%202021)%20a%20higher%20percentage%20of%20men%20marrying%20more%20than%20one%20wife%20than%20the%20Muslims%20in%20the%20state%3F%20So%20far%20as%20one%20knows%2C%20there%20was%20no%20well%20publicised%20and%20wide%20dialogue%20between%20citizens%E2%80%99%20groups%20(especially%20the%20women%20whom%20it%20impacts%20the%20most)%20and%20the%20creators%20of%20the%20draft.%20Due%20care%20was%20also%20not%20taken%20to%20depoliticise%20the%20Bill%20by%20placing%20it%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20not%20before%20but%20after%20the%20general%20elections.%20Can%20we%20then%20pooh-pooh%20women%E2%80%99s%20groups%20and%20the%20Muslim%20minority%20seeing%20it%20as%20a%20political%20move%20to%20consolidate%20majority%20votes%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Not%20in%20the%20Name%20of%20Gender%20Justice%3A%20Reflections%20on%20Uttarakhand's%20UCC%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnot-in-the-name-of-gender-justice-reflections-on-the-uttarakhands-ucc%5C%22%3ENot%20in%20the%20Name%20of%20Gender%20Justice%3A%20Reflections%20on%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20UCC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20obvious%2C%20as%20the%20press%20note%20from%20the%20dissenting%20group%20of%20women%20says%2C%20that%20the%20State%20can%20now%20reach%20deep%20inside%20personal%20spaces%2C%20even%20invade%20the%20privacy%20of%20citizens%E2%80%99%20bedrooms.%20Supporters%20deem%20the%20UCC%20a%20progressive%20step%20that%20would%20protect%20women%20in%20live-in%20relationships%20against%20domestic%20violence%20and%20confer%20legitimacy%20and%20property%20rights%20on%20any%20children%20born%20out%20of%20wedlock.%20But%20these%20provisions%20already%20existed%20under%20the%20federal%20laws%20such%20as%20the%20Domestic%20Violence%20Act.%20And%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20already%20ruled%20that%20live-in%20relationships%20are%20not%20criminal.%20Goa%20has%20had%20a%20pre-independence%20UCC%20that%20protects%20such%20unions.%20Did%20the%20draft%20makers%20even%20consult%20that%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20more%20unsettling%20is%20that%20the%20government%20has%20not%20only%20not%20created%20widespread%20awareness%20about%20the%20hows%20and%20whys%20about%20new%20provisions%20of%20the%20UCC%2C%20it%20has%20also%20not%20produced%20necessary%20documentation%20to%20pass%20around%20among%20citizens.%20This%20means%20that%20many%20people%2C%20especially%20the%20young%20men%20and%20women%2C%20may%20find%20that%20they%20are%20law%20violators%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20State%20because%20they%20have%20not%20submitted%20necessary%20documentation%20to%20a%20registrar%20within%2030%20days%20of%20their%20union.%20This%20failure%20may%20subject%20them%20to%20heavy%20penalties%20and%20even%20long%20jail%20sentences%2C%20without%20being%20told%20in%20clear%20terms%20how%20and%20why.%20In%20a%20state%20with%20a%20small%20but%20diverse%20population%20following%20various%20faiths%20and%20personal%20laws%2C%20with%20a%20sizeable%20rural%20population%20living%20in%20remote%20areas%2C%20any%20information%20needs%20time%20to%20reach%20and%20be%20absorbed%20by%20the%20locals.%20A%20sudden%20imposition%20of%20a%20UCC%20can%20trigger%20immediate%20and%20unforeseen%20social%2C%20political%2C%20legal%20and%20constitutional%20implications%20for%20Uttarakhandis.%20With%20the%20prolonged%20vituperative%20talk%20against%20%E2%80%98love%20jihad%E2%80%99%20and%20repeated%20underlining%20in%20media%20messages%20about%20how%20the%20law%20will%20free%20Muslim%20women%20of%20%3Cem%3Ehalala%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Eiddat%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20bigamy%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20intent%20is%20more%20political%20than%20reformist%20and%20protective%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20intent%2C%20the%20UCC%20can%20not%20be%20faulted.%20It%20proposes%20to%20standardise%20the%20minimum%20age%20of%20marriage%20for%20all%20(already%20standardised%20for%20most%20citizens)%2C%20outlaw%20extra-judicial%20marital%20norms%20that%20exploited%20women%2C%20prohibit%20polygamy%20and%20promise%20equal%20inheritance%20to%20both%20men%20and%20women.%20Given%20how%20women%20have%20been%20exploited%20along%20these%20issues%2C%20there%20is%20no%20denying%20the%20UCC%20is%20in%20itself%20a%20good%20idea.%20But%20the%20present%20UCC%20law%20is%20full%20of%20holes.%20Take%20the%20mandatory%20registration%20(within%2030%20days)%20of%20the%20relationship%20and%20the%20punitive%20proceedings%20that%20will%20follow%20swiftly%20in%20case%20of%20failure%20to%20do%20so.%20The%20lack%20of%20public%20awareness%20about%20the%20new%20laws%20can%20easily%20hand%20the%20State%20a%20new%20tool%20and%20if%20it%20so%20desires%2C%20to%20cherry%20pick%20political%20dissenters%20and%20minorities%20to%20harass%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Centre%20opposed%20same-sex%20marriage%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20it%20did%20so%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20the%20concept%20of%20marriage%20is%20inherently%20connected%20to%20religious%20and%20cultural%20norms.%20Why%20has%20this%20autonomy%20for%20religio-cultural%20norms%20suddenly%20been%20discarded%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20registrar%20criminalising%20live-in%20relationships%20because%20the%20couple%20may%20have%20come%20to%20him%20not%20within%20the%20mandated%20period%3F%20Also%20it%20is%20unclear%20when%20couples%20go%20to%20him%20how%20he%20will%20verify%20the%20details%20provided%20by%20them.%20He%20may%20choose%20someone%20who%20can%20%E2%80%9Cconduct%20enquiry%20to%20establish%20validity%20of%20the%20relationship%E2%80%9D.%20The%20use%20of%20phrases%20to%20describe%20prohibited%20relationships%20under%20titles%20like%20%E2%80%98legitimate%20blood%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98half%20blood%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98uterine%20blood%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98full%20blood%E2%80%99%20in%20an%20actual%20legal%20document%20is%20mind%20boggling%20to%20say%20the%20least.%20Who%20can%20the%20registrar%20summon%20when%20judging%20a%20case%20of%20live-in%20relationship%3F%20An%20angry%20parent%20%3F%20A%20cousin%20with%20a%20score%20to%20settle%3F%20An%20RWA%20uncle%20who%20brought%20it%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20registrar%20who%20maintains%20the%20register%20of%20all%20such%20couples%3F%20The%20local%20Thanadhyaksh%20ji%3F%20Is%20the%20registrar%20allowed%20to%20share%20this%20register%20of%20couples%20in%20live-in%20relationship%20with%20the%20local%20police%20station%3F%20Is%20it%20a%20public%20register%20anyone%20can%20access%20like%20other%20registers%20listed%20in%20the%20new%20law%20(Part%201%2C%20Chapter%202)%20pertaining%20to%20marriages%2C%20divorces%20etc.%3F%20If%20it%20is%2C%20what%20prevents%20the%20local%20moral%20policing%20groups%20from%20intruding%20into%20the%20bedrooms%20of%20%E2%80%98suspected%E2%80%99%20citizens%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20time%20to%20recall%20that%20the%20State%20has%20not%20created%20either%20the%20institution%20of%20marriage%20or%20live-in%20relationships.%20Society%20and%20the%20changing%20times%20have.%20Each%20law%20is%20a%20society%E2%80%99s%20text%2C%20a%20reflection%20of%20its%20rational%20mind.%20But%20our%20judiciary%2C%20legislature%2C%20executive%20and%20the%20media%20are%20all%20glaringly%20minority%20and%20female%20deficient.%20So%20even%20if%20we%20believe%20in%20the%20milk%20of%20human%20kindness%20flowing%20in%20the%20State%E2%80%99s%20veins%2C%20the%20State%20must%20show%20proof%20of%20its%20sincerity%20in%20recognising%20the%20enormity%20and%20complexity%20of%20the%20task%20of%20giving%20us%20a%20just%20and%20fair%20%C2%A0UCC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3ESaakhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20Sunday%20column%20from%20Mrinal%20Pande%2C%20in%20which%20she%20writes%20of%20what%20she%20sees%20and%20also%20participates%20in.%20That%20has%20been%20her%20burden%20to%20bear%20ever%20since%20she%20embarked%20on%20a%20life%20as%20a%20journalist%2C%20writer%2C%20editor%2C%20author%20and%20as%20chairperson%20of%20Prasar%20Bharti.%20Her%20journey%20of%20being%20a%20witness-participant%20continues.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707647447000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F07131439%2FIMG_0107-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftalking-uniform-civil-code%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20its%20intent%2C%20the%20UCC%20can%20not%20be%20faulted.%20But%20the%20present%20Uttarakhand%20UCC%20law%20is%20full%20of%20holes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22