2author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Boroline%20Saga%3A%20From%20a%20Symbol%20of%20the%20Swadeshi%20Movement%20to%20a%20Bengali%20Household%20Staple%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11155422%2FBoroline_Antiseptic_Cream.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20On%20August%2015%2C%201947%2C%20when%20India%20gained%20independence%20from%20British%20rule%2C%20two%20of%20Calcutta%E2%80%99s%20newspapers%20announced%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fboroline.com%2Fabout-boroline%2F%5C%22%3Eone%20lakh%20Boroline%20tubes%20would%20be%20distributed%20for%20free%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoroline%20was%20first%20launched%20in%201929%20by%20a%20Bengali%20merchant%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F173787%2Fbengal-boroline-gd-pharmaceutical-swadeshi-movement-india%2F%5C%22%3EGour%20Mohun%20Dutta.%3C%2Fa%3E%20It%20was%20then%20colloquially%20called%20%3Cem%3Ehaatiwala%3C%2Fem%3E%20cream%20(the%20cream%20with%20the%20elephant)%20because%20of%20its%20iconic%20white%20elephant%20logo%20on%20the%20green%20cover.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20the%20product%20has%20managed%20to%20weather%20the%20eddy%20and%20flow%20of%20market%20change%20and%20is%20still%20just%20as%20relevant%20today%20as%20it%20was%2095%20years%20ago.%20Against%20all%20odds%2C%20Boroline%20was%20introduced%20in%20the%20colonial%20Indian%20market%20as%20an%20effective%20and%20potent%20alternative%20to%20imported%20foreign%20creams.%20Coupled%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhomegrown.co.in%2Fhomegrown-voices%2Fswadeshi-identity-bengali-nostalgia-the-history-of-indias-first-antiseptic-cream%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Swadeshi%E2%80%99%20sentiments%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20an%20effort%20to%20promote%20India%E2%80%99s%20economic%20self-sufficiency%2C%20Boroline%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20soon%20swept%20over%20the%20entire%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20amidst%20the%20fervour%20of%20Swadeshi%20sentiments%2C%20Indians%20readily%20boycotted%20all%20foreign%20goods%20and%20embraced%20this%20multipurpose%20antiseptic%20cream%20that%20entered%20the%20market%20at%20that%20opportune%20moment%20at%20a%20cheap%20price.%20During%20the%20Second%20World%20War%2C%20G.D.%20Pharmaceutical%20sold%20the%20cream%20in%20any%20container%20available%2C%20with%20a%20label%20at%20the%20bottom%20that%20promised%2C%20%E2%80%9COriginal%20packing%20changed%20due%20to%20war%20emergency%2C%20quantity%20and%20quality%20of%20contents%20remain%20unaltered.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20small%20cut%20wounds%2C%20scabs%2C%20chapped%20and%20dried%20skin%20to%20extra%20moisturisation%20during%20chilly%20weather%20%E2%80%93%20a%20thick%20layer%20of%20Boroline%20cream%20soon%20became%20a%20one-stop%20solution%20for%20all%20skin-related%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHenceforth%2C%20the%20product%20became%20synonymous%20with%20Indian%20cultural%20identity%2C%20serving%20folks%20living%20in%20the%20cold%20Himalayan%20regions%20and%20the%20Southern%20plains%20of%20the%20country%2C%20with%20the%20same%20measure%20of%20effectiveness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20curious%20thing%20about%20this%20product%20is%20its%20enduring%20popularity%20against%20the%20plethora%20of%20multinational%20brands%20that%20have%20been%20flooding%20the%20market%20with%20innovative%20formulations%20every%20few%20months.%20The%20antiseptic%20formula%20of%20Boroline%20%E2%80%93%20boric%20acid%20mixed%20with%20zinc%20oxide%20%3Cem%3E(jasad%20bhasma%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20paraffin%20and%20oleum%2C%20infused%20with%20a%20unique%20fragrance%20%E2%80%93%20is%20hardly%20a%20secret.%20Yet%20a%20deluge%20of%20innovative%20skincare%20products%20and%20counterfeit%20products%20entering%20the%20market%20every%20year%20fails%20to%20dupe%20Boroline%20users%2C%20without%20any%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20for%20a%20brand%20with%20Boroline%E2%80%99s%20equity%2C%20it%20generates%20a%20yearly%20revenue%20of%20only%20Rs%20150%20crore%2C%20which%20is%20quite%20underwhelming%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2FHome-Page%2FlPdtZPKn9F1l2OZogkJSoJ%2FIts-business-as-usual-for-87yearold-Boroline.html%5C%22%3ERoopen%20Roy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20former%20managing%20director%20of%20Deloitte%20Consulting%20India%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDebashish%20Dutta%2C%20grandson%20of%20Gour%20Mohun%20Dutta%2C%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2FCompanies%2FBvkIFoi2YFIY7RtiarEaRN%2FOur-thrust-will-be-on-expanding-Boroline-Suthols-retail-pe.html%5C%22%3ELivemint%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20made%20sure%20that%20our%20successful%20products%20are%20consistent%E2%80%94they%20don%E2%80%99t%20change.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20have%20found%20that%20such%20a%20conservative%20attitude%20towards%20change%20is%20a%20common%20trait%20in%20most%20Bengali%20business%20ventures.%20They%20tend%20to%20target%20a%20very%20specific%20and%20old%20customer%20base%2C%20focusing%20more%20on%20quality%20than%20the%20numbers%20on%20the%20profit%20scale%20and%20refusing%20to%20compete%20with%20short-term%20market%20trends.%20Their%20reservation%20towards%20scaling%20up%20is%20quite%20possibly%20a%20precautionary%20response%20to%20the%20immense%20loss%20once%20incurred%20by%20the%20Bengali%20merchants%20during%20their%20trade%20with%20the%20British%20in%20the%20colonial%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20G.D.%20Pharma%E2%80%99s%202003%20launch%2C%20the%20antiseptic%20liquid%20Suthol%2C%20has%20diversified%20its%20market%20and%20is%20rapidly%20growing%20in%20popularity.%20It%20accounts%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2FHome-Page%2FlPdtZPKn9F1l2OZogkJSoJ%2FIts-business-as-usual-for-87yearold-Boroline.html%5C%22%3E30%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20GD%20Pharma%E2%80%99s%20sales%20currently%2C%20showing%20remarkable%20growth%20on%20a%20year-on-year%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EG.D.%20Pharma%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20consistency%20has%20been%20equivocally%20rewarded%20by%20its%20customer%20base%2C%20even%20by%20the%20globe-trotting%20Bengali%20communities%20of%20the%20present%20day.%20Multiple%20tubs%20of%20Boroline%20go%20through%20customs%20at%20various%20airports%20every%20year%20when%20Bengalis%20move%20abroad%20for%20study%20or%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuchetana%20Chatterjee%2C%20a%20student%20living%20in%20Munich%2C%20swears%20by%20Boroline%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20tried%20tons%20of%20skincare%20products%2C%20and%20in%20-10%20degrees%2C%20nothing%20works%20as%20good%20as%20Boroline%2C%20also%20vouched%20for%20by%20some%20of%20my%20international%20friends!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShorbori%20Biswas%2C%20currently%20living%20in%20Georgia%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20use%20Boroline%20in%20Tbilisi%20as%20well%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20best%20for%20dry%20skin%20like%20mine.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanjini%20Mahalanobish%2C%20who%20has%20been%20living%20in%20Philadelphia%20for%20a%20few%20years%20now%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20stock%20up%20on%20%5BBoroline%5D%20on%20each%20visit%20to%20India.%20Its%20proven%20effectiveness%20and%20affordability%20make%20it%20my%20go-to%20choice%2C%20echoing%20a%20habit%20passed%20on%20by%20my%20grandparents.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnwesha%20Das%2C%20a%20student%20at%20TU%20Delft%2C%20Netherlands%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20brought%20along%20five%20tubs%20to%20last%20me%20as%20long%20as%20I%20was%20away%20from%20home.%20Mum%20and%20I%20applying%20Boroline%20on%20our%20elbows%20and%20lips%20had%20been%20our%20nighttime%20ritual%20long%20before%20these%20popular%20skincare%20potions%20hit%20the%20market%20and%20this%20is%20a%20habit%20I%E2%80%99d%20never%20grow%20out%20of.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bengali%20community%E2%80%99s%20close%20relationship%20with%20the%20moss-green%20tube%20of%20Boroline%20is%20laced%20with%20a%20hint%20of%20nostalgia%2C%20community%20pride%2C%20and%20faith%20in%20a%20product%20that%20has%20been%20passed%20down%20through%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDebabratee%20Dhar%20was%20an%20intern%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Wire%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707647131000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11155422%2FBoroline_Antiseptic_Cream.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fthe-boroline-saga-from-a-symbol-of-the-swadeshi-movement-to-a-bengali-household-staple%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22G.D.%20Pharma%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20consistency%20has%20been%20equivocally%20rewarded%20by%20its%20customer%20base%2C%20even%20by%20the%20globe-trotting%20Bengali%20communities%20of%20the%20present%20day.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fthe-boroline-saga-from-a-symbol-of-the-swadeshi-movement-to-a-bengali-household-staple%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Violent%20protests%20erupt%20in%20Senegal%20against%20delayed%20presidential%20elections%3B%203%20dead%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707647126000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107600779%2Cimgsize-1398658.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fviolent-protests-erupt-in-senegal-against-delayed-presidential-elections-3-dead%2Farticleshow%2F107600580.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107600580.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EPresident%20Sall%20has%20justified%20the%20election%20postponement%20by%20citing%20a%20dispute%20between%20parliament%20and%20the%20