d%20to%20end%20in%20the%20next%2010-20%20days%2C%20and%20we%20have%20extended%20that%20by%20another%2010%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReels%20shot%20by%20doctors%20have%20gone%20viral%20on%20several%20occasions%20in%20the%20recent%20past%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20post-Covid%20era.%20These%20reels%20have%20sharply%20divided%20public%20opinion.%20While%20many%20have%20praised%20doctors%20for%20their%20moves%20and%20seen%20the%20reels%20as%20a%20way%20to%20counter%20work%20stress%2C%20others%20have%20questioned%20if%20such%20conduct%20reflect%20negligence%20towards%20their%20work%20and%20inconvenienced%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707637620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fi40feqo_gadag-institute_625x300_11_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgadag-institute-of-medical-sciences-38-junior-doctors-face-action-over-viral-reels-shot-in-karnataka-college-5036221%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20government%20medical%20college%20in%20Karnataka's%20Gadag%20has%20cracked%20down%20on%20junior%20doctors%20recording%20reels%20on%20campus.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgadag-institute-of-medical-sciences-38-junior-doctors-face-action-over-viral-reels-shot-in-karnataka-college-5036221%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgadag-institute-of-medical-sciences-38-junior-doctors-face-action-over-viral-reels-shot-in-karnataka-college-5036221%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgadag-institute-of-medical-sciences-38-junior-doctors-face-action-over-viral-reels-shot-in-karnataka-college-5036221%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Iran%20celebrates%2045th%20anniversary%20of%20Islamic%20Revolution%20as%20conflict%20grips%20Middle%20East%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%2