nt%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F31153655%2FUntitled-design-8-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJalandhar%2FChandigarh%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20scheduled%20%E2%80%98Delhi%20Chalo%E2%80%99%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20on%20February%2013%2C%20the%20Haryana%20government%20on%20Saturday%20evening%20announced%20the%20suspension%20of%20mobile%20internet%20services%20from%20February%2011%20to%20February%2013%20in%20Ambala%2C%20Kurukshetra%2C%20Kaithal%2C%20Jind%2C%20Hisar%2C%20Fatehabad%20and%20Sirsa%20including%20Dabwali%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20from%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20the%20newly%20floated%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Morcha%20(KMM)%20led%20by%20senior%20farmers%E2%80%99%20leader%20from%20the%20Samyukt%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(SKM)%20non-political%20and%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Sangharsh%20Committee%20(KMSC)%20president%20Sarvan%20Singh%20Pandher%20are%20organising%20the%20February%2013%20%E2%80%98Delhi%20Chalo%E2%80%99%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20order%2C%20additional%20chief%20secretary%2C%20Haryana%20government%20T.V.S.N.%20Prasad%20said%20that%20in%20view%20of%20the%20call%20for%20a%20farmers%E2%80%99%20march%2Fagitation%20given%20by%20certain%20organisations%2C%E2%80%9DThere%20is%20a%20clear%20potential%20of%20disruption%20of%20public%20utilities%2C%20damage%20to%20public%20assets%20and%20amenities%20and%20disturbance%20of%20public%20law%20and%20order%20in%20above%20mentioned%20districts%20on%20account%20of%20misuse%20of%20internet%20services%20by%20way%20of%20spread%20of%20inflammatory%20material%20and%20false%20rumours%2C%20which%20are%20being%2Fcould%20be%20transmitted%2Fcirculated%20to%20the%20public%20through%20social%20media%2Fmessaging%20services%20on%20mobile%20internet%20services%2C%20SMS%20services%20and%20other%20dongle%20services.%E2%80%9D%20All%20Haryana%20telecom%20operators%20have%20been%20directed%20to%20ensure%20compliance%20with%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20has%20been%20passed%20under%20Section%205%20of%20Indian%20Telegraph%20Act%2C%201885%20and%20Rule%202%20of%20temporary%20suspension%20of%20Telecom%20Services%20(Public%20Emergency%20or%20Public%20Safety)%20Rules%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20further%20read%2C%C2%A0%E2%80%9CI%20hereby%20order%20the%20suspension%20of%20the%20mobile%20internet%20services%2C%20bulk%20SMS%20(excluding%20banking%20and%20mobile%20recharge)%20and%20all%20dongle%20services%20etc.%20provided%20on%20mobile%20networks%20except%20the%20voice%20calls%20in%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20districts%20Ambala%2C%20Kurukshetra%2C%20Kaithal%2C%20Jind%2C%20Hisar%2C%20Fatehabad%20and%20Sirsa%20of%20Haryana%20State.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20message%20on%20X%2C%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Morcha%20(KMM)%2C%20coordinator%20and%20the%20president%20of%20KMSC%20Sarvan%20Singh%20Pandher%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20got%20to%20know%20from%20the%20media%20that%20the%20Haryana%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20suspend%20internet%20services%2C%20which%20is%20totally%20inhumane.%20Converting%20Haryana%20into%20an%20open%20jail%20is%20not%20good.%20This%20cannot%20be%20the%20decision%20of%20a%20democratically%20elected%20government.%20On%20one%20hand%20the%20Central%20govt%20is%20talking%20to%20farmers%20through%20the%20Punjab%20government%20and%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20they%20are%20conducting%20raids%20and%20creating%20trouble%20for%20our%20women.%20We%20condemn%20the%20Haryana%20government%E2%80%99s%20attitude.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandher%20also%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20appeal%20to%20the%20Haryana%20people%20and%20farmers%20that%20the%20entire%20country%20and%20Punjab%20stand%20with%20them.%20%3Cem%3EHum%20log%20peaceful%20tarike%20se%20February%2013%20ka%20protest%20karenge%2C%20jo%20%E2%80%98aar-paar%E2%80%99%20ka%20hoga%3C%2Fem%3E%20(We%20will%20lead%20the%20February%2013%20protest%20peacefully%2C%20which%20will%20be%20a%20do%20or%20die%20battle).%20We%20have%20also%20conveyed%20to%20the%20mediators%20between%20farmers%20and%20the%20Centre%20to%20ask%20the%20Haryana%20DGP%20to%20stop%20all%20that%20they%20are%20doing%20to%20target%20farmers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20internet%20ban%20order%2C%20Ranjit%20Singh%20Raju%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Gramin%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Samiti%2C%20Sri%20Ganganagar%20district%2C%20Rajasthan%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CFarmers%20do%20not%20need%20any%20network%20for%20their%20protest.%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20own%20network%20is%20very%20strong.%20Rather%20this%20is%20a%20congratulatory%20sign%20for%20us.%20Modi%20government%20is%20afraid%2C%20hence%20indulging%20in%20such%20tactics.%20Farmers%20will%20be%20moving%20to%20Delhi%20on%20February%2013.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20internet%20ban%20order%20came%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20first%20round%20of%20talks%20between%20a%20delegation%20of%20the%20Central%20government%2C%20Punjab%20chief%20minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20and%20farmers%E2%80%99%20union%20leaders%2C%20who%20met%20in%20Chandigarh%20on%20February%208.%20Union%20ministers%20Piyush%20Goyal%2C%20Arjun%20Munda%20and%20Nityanand%20Rai%20had%20assured%20the%20farmers%20that%20they%20would%20discuss%20their%20demands%20with%20the%20ministries%20concerned.%20Even%20the%20Punjab%20chief%20minister%20had%20claimed%20that%20farmers%20and%20the%20government%20had%20reached%20a%20consensus%20on%20their%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20the%20KMM%20gave%20a%20call%20for%20the%20Delhi%20Chalo%20protest%2C%20farmers%20across%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20have%20been%20gearing%20up%20for%20the%20march.%20Farmers%20have%20been%20gathering%20dry%20ration%20for%20six%20months%2C%20tents%2C%20beds%2C%20fans%20and%20other%20essentials%20in%20the%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Haryana%20police%20has%20barricaded%20highways%20leading%20to%20Delhi%20and%20was%20also%20conducted%20late%20night%20raids%20on%20the%20houses%20of%20the%20farmers.%20%E2%80%9CHaryana%20police%20are%20reaching%20our%20houses%20without%20lady%20police%20late%20at%20night%20and%20questioning%20our%20women%20about%20our%20whereabouts.%20We%20are%20being%20targeted%20just%20because%20we%20are%20raising%20our%20voice%20against%20PM%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20dictatorial%20attitude.%20The%20Modi%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20implement%20MSP%20law%2C%20justice%20to%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20victims%2C%20compensation%20to%20farmers%20martyred%20in%20farmers%20agitations%20and%20pension%20for%20their%20welfare.%20We%20will%20not%20sit%20quietly%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20farmers%E2%80%99%20union%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20some%20of%20the%20big%20farmers%E2%80%99%20unions%20including%20BKU%20Ugrahan%20and%20original%20SKM%20faction%20under%20Dr%20Darshan%20Pal%2C%20Yadvindra%20Yadav%20and%20others%20distanced%20themselves%20from%20the%20%E2%80%98Dilli%20Chalo%E2%80%99%20protest%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20last%20week%2C%20SKM%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20national%20coordination%20committee%20of%20SKM%20held%20an%20online%20meeting%20and%20clarified%20that%20SKM%20has%20not%20given%20any%20call%20for%20%E2%80%98Dilli%20Chalo%E2%80%99.%20SKM%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20decision%20of%20certain%20kisan%20organisations%20to%20protest%20in%20Delhi%20on%20February%2013.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Jagjit%20Singh%20Dallewal%E2%80%99s%20SKM%20(non-political)%20faction%20believes%20that%20once%20their%20protest%20reaches%20Delhi%2C%20all%20major%20unions%20will%20join%20them%20since%20the%20issues%20they%20are%20fighting%20for%20are%20genuine%20and%20legitimate.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707636669000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F31153655%2FUntitled-design-8-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Finternet-suspended-in-7-haryana-districts-as-farmers-plan-for-delhi-chalo-protest%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Several%