terindia.com%2F329424%2Fludhiana-woman-grows-200-plants-in-terrace-garden-watch-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20flowers%20are%20dried%3C%2Fa%3E%20without%20further%20processing%3B%20%E2%80%98Mongra%20Saffron%E2%80%99%20is%20the%20variety%20where%20stigmas%20are%20detached%20from%20the%20flower%2C%20dried%20in%20the%20sun%2C%20and%20processed%20traditionally%3B%20and%20%E2%80%98Guchhi%20Saffron%E2%80%99%20which%20also%20does%20not%20involve%20the%20stigmas%20being%20processed.%20Instead%2C%20they%20are%20dried%20and%20joined%20in%20a%20bundle%20tied%20with%20a%20cloth%20thread.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20that%20the%20Patels%20are%20growing%20is%20the%20second%20variety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20first%20harvest%20was%20an%20experiment%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vaibhav%20emphasises.%20But%20lucrative%20all%20the%20same.%20Each%20gram%20of%20the%20red%20threads%20fetched%20the%20couple%20Rs%20700.%20As%20for%20the%20road%20ahead%2C%20they%20are%20confident%20they%20can%20expand%20sales%20implementing%20the%20learnings%20of%20the%20previous%20harvest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707485452000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG_0318_11zon-1707478888.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D341322%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22How%20to%20grow%20saffron%20at%20home%3F%20Vaibhav%20Patel%20and%20Aastha%20Maheshwari%20Patel%20have%20transformed%20their%20Vadodara%20home%20into%20a%20Kashmiri%20saffron%20haven%2C%20defying%20geographical%20norms.%20They%20share%20insights%20into%20the%20intricate%20process%20of%20growing%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20expensive%20spice%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Search%20for%20runner%20and%20mum-of-thre